1
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,430
<font size=24>1462年</font>
The year, 1462.

2
00:00:43,300 --> 00:00:45,670
<font size=24>康斯坦丁堡陷落</font>
Constantinople had fallen.

3
00:00:46,510 --> 00:00:50,240
<font size=24>信奉回教的土耳其人大军横扫欧洲</font>
Moslem Turks swept into Europe with a vast, superior force...

4
00:00:50,510 --> 00:00:54,500
<font size=24>痛击罗马尼亚威胁整个基督教世界</font>
striking at Romania, threatening all of Christendom.

5
00:00:54,680 --> 00:00:59,220
<font size=24>川索凡尼亚有一名圣龙会武士</font>
From Transylvania arose a Romanian knight of the Sacred Order of the Dragon,

6
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:01,920
<font size=24>名叫德古拉</font>
known as Dracula.

7
00:01:17,870 --> 00:01:20,140
<font size=24>战役前夕</font>
On the eve of the battle...

8
00:01:20,270 --> 00:01:25,940
<font size=24>他挚爱的新娘伊丽莎白</font>
his bride Elisabeta whom he prized above all things on Earth...

9
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:30,480
<font size=24>知道他将与强敌对阵</font>
knew that he must face an insurmountable force...

10
00:01:30,820 --> 00:01:34,150
<font size=24>可能一去不返</font>
from which he might never return.

11
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:33,940
<font size=24>(赞美主)</font>

12
00:02:34,010 --> 00:02:35,950
<font size=24>(我已获胜)</font>

13
00:02:45,630 --> 00:02:47,620
<font size=24>伊丽莎白</font>
Elisabeta.

14
00:02:50,460 --> 00:02:53,960
<font size=24>诡诈的土耳其军射箭入城</font>
The vengeful Turks shot an arrow into the castle...

15
00:02:54,470 --> 00:02:57,560
<font size=24>散布德古拉阵亡的谣言</font>
carrying false news of Dracula's death.

16
00:02:57,910 --> 00:03:00,570
<font size=24>伊丽莎白信以为真</font>
Elisabeta, believing him dead...

17
00:03:00,810 --> 00:03:03,470
<font size=24>投河自尽</font>
flung herself into the river.

18
00:03:42,350 --> 00:03:44,340
<font size=24>我的王子死了</font>
My prince is dead.

19
00:03:44,950 --> 00:03:47,080
<font size=24>没有他一切都毫无意义</font>
All is lost without him.

20
00:03:47,750 --> 00:03:50,090
<font size=24>但愿能在天上重逢</font>
May God unite us in heaven.

21
00:04:04,570 --> 00:04:06,630
<font size=24>(她是自尽死的)</font>

22
00:04:07,110 --> 00:04:09,580
<font size=24>(她的灵魂不能升天堂)</font>

23
00:04:10,710 --> 00:04:11,770
<font size=24>(要受天谴)</font>

24
00:04:12,910 --> 00:04:14,780
<font size=24>(这是神的律令)</font>

25
00:04:23,990 --> 00:04:27,450
<font size=24>(这就是我捍卫教会的报偿吗?)</font>

26
00:04:27,530 --> 00:04:28,520
<font size=24>(放肆)</font>

27
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:32,330
<font size=24>(我唾弃上帝)</font>

28
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:36,860
<font size=24>(我将死后复生)</font>

29
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:41,610
<font size=24>(用尽邪恶力量为她复仇)</font>

30
00:04:59,500 --> 00:05:02,430
<font size=24>(血是生命泉源)</font>

31
00:05:03,300 --> 00:05:07,360
<font size=24>(我将饮血维生)</font>

32
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:43,660
<font size=24>吸血鬼惊情四百年</font>

33
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:54,410
<font size=24>伦敦,1897年</font>

34
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:58,470
<font size=24>四个世纪后</font>

35
00:05:59,020 --> 00:06:02,890
<font size=24>(卡费斯区精神病院)</font>

36
00:06:03,220 --> 00:06:06,750
<font size=24>我都照你的吩咐做了,主人</font>
I've done everything that you asked, master.

37
00:06:08,230 --> 00:06:11,560
<font size=24>一切准备就绪</font>
All the preparations are in order.

38
00:06:11,630 --> 00:06:13,330
<font size=24>万事俱全</font>
Everything.

39
00:06:13,430 --> 00:06:15,900
<font size=24>我等待你的命令</font>
I await your command.

40
00:06:16,340 --> 00:06:17,890
<font size=24>因为</font>
For I know...

41
00:06:19,110 --> 00:06:21,770
<font size=24>当你论功行赏时</font>
that when the rewards are given...

42
00:06:22,340 --> 00:06:26,180
<font size=24>你的慷慨会使我受益无穷</font>
I will be one of those who benefits from your generosity.

43
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:32,850
<font size=24>谢谢</font>
Thank you.

44
00:06:35,020 --> 00:06:37,620
<font size=24>伦费发狂了</font>
Gone mad. Renfield is deranged.

45
00:06:39,460 --> 00:06:41,520
<font size=24>心智丧失</font>
He's lost his greedy mind, poor chap.

46
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:46,590
<font size=24>替个外国人德古拉伯爵理财</font>
I want you to take over for his foreign client this rather eccentric Count Dracula.

47
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,930
<font size=24>他要在伦敦近郊买房产</font>
- He's buying up property around London. - Of course, sir.

48
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:52,870
<font size=24>我会转告伯爵,谢谢你的委派</font>
I'll attend to the count. Thank you for your confidence.

49
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:55,940
<font size=24>这是你的大好良机,哈克</font>
This is a great opportunity for you, Harker.

50
00:06:56,140 --> 00:06:59,200
<font size=24>但你必须立刻前往川索凡尼亚</font>
But you'll have to leave for Transylvania immediately.

51
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:03,080
<font size=24>终生难遇的机会</font>
Opportunities such as this come but once in a lifetime.

52
00:07:03,420 --> 00:07:05,180
<font size=24>那当然</font>
Yes, of course, sir.

53
00:07:05,520 --> 00:07:10,010
<font size=24>伦费先生在川索凡尼亚怎么了</font>
If I may inquire...what, in fact, happened to Mr. Renfield in Transylvania?

54
00:07:11,020 --> 00:07:13,020
<font size=24>没什么</font>
Nothing. Nothing.

55
00:07:13,260 --> 00:07:15,250
<font size=24>私人问题</font>
Personal problems.

56
00:07:15,460 --> 00:07:20,600
<font size=24>完成这些交易你在公司的前途无量</font>
Close these transactions...and your future with this firm is assured.

57
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:23,690
<font size=24>是,我会全力以赴</font>
Yes, sir. I will give it my full attention.

58
00:07:27,670 --> 00:07:29,940
<font size=24>我们等了那么久</font>
We've waited this long, haven't we?

59
00:07:30,510 --> 00:07:32,600
<font size=24>我一回来就结婚</font>
We can be married when I return.

60
00:07:35,020 --> 00:07:36,000
<font size=24>好吧</font>
Of course.

61
00:07:36,620 --> 00:07:38,020
<font size=24>我会写信的</font>
I'll write.

62
00:07:39,350 --> 00:07:40,680
<font size=24>强纳生</font>
Jonathan.

63
00:07:45,860 --> 00:07:47,790
<font size=24>强纳生,我爱你</font>
Jonathan, I love you.

64
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:49,520
<font size=24>我爱你,米娜</font>
I love you, Mina.

65
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:22,560
<font size=24>5月25日,布达佩斯</font>
25th May, Budapest.

66
00:08:22,730 --> 00:08:25,060
<font size=24>今晨离开布达佩斯</font>
Left Budapest early this morning.

67
00:08:25,300 --> 00:08:26,820
<font size=24>依我看...</font>
The impression I had was that we were leaving the west...

68
00:08:26,900 --> 00:08:31,030
<font size=24>我们是往东欧前进(强纳生哈克之日记)</font>
and entering the east.

69
00:08:31,100 --> 00:08:34,510
<font size=24>这一带是罗马尼亚最东部</font>
The district I am to enter is in the extreme east of the country...

70
00:08:34,740 --> 00:08:39,210
<font size=24>摩达维亚、布卡维纳及川索凡尼亚</font>
just on the borders of three states...Transylvania, Moldavia and Bukovina...

71
00:08:39,350 --> 00:08:41,410
<font size=24>喀尔巴阡山交界处</font>
in the midst of the Carpathian Mountains...

72
00:08:41,580 --> 00:08:44,910
<font size=24>欧洲最荒凉无名的一区</font>
one of the wildest and least known portions of Europe.

73
00:08:48,090 --> 00:08:49,680
<font size=24>朋友</font>
"My friend...

74
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:53,250
<font size=24>欢迎到喀尔巴阡山</font>
welcome to the Carpathians.

75
00:08:53,860 --> 00:08:56,520
<font size=24>久候大驾多时</font>
I am anxiously expecting you.

76
00:08:57,100 --> 00:08:58,930
<font size=24>我的马车</font>
At the Borgo Pass...

77
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:02,430
<font size=24>将在波戈隘口等你</font>
my carriage will await you and bring you to me.

78
00:09:03,270 --> 00:09:07,210
<font size=24>深信你一路顺畅</font>
I trust yourjourney from London has been a happy one...

79
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:10,700
<font size=24>并希望你在我国</font>
and that you will enjoy your stay...

80
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:13,370
<font size=24>身心愉快</font>
in my beautiful land.

81
00:09:14,110 --> 00:09:15,600
<font size=24>你的朋友敬上</font>
Your friend,

82
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,850
<font size=24>德</font>
D."

83
00:09:26,460 --> 00:09:28,950
<font size=24>5月25日,日记</font>
Diary, 25th May.

84
00:09:29,630 --> 00:09:32,890
<font size=24>亲爱的强纳生离去近一周(米娜墨瑞之日记)</font>
My Jonathan has been gone almost a week.

85
00:09:33,170 --> 00:09:36,760
<font size=24>我虽因不能立刻成婚感到失望</font>
And although I was disappointed we could not marry before his departure...

86
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:40,230
<font size=24>仍为他出使重要任务而高兴</font>
I am happy that he got sent on this important assignment.

87
00:09:40,410 --> 00:09:42,900
<font size=24>我渴望他的音讯</font>
I am longing to hear all the news.

88
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:46,180
<font size=24>到外国一定很有趣</font>
It must be so nice to see strange countries.

89
00:09:47,310 --> 00:09:52,710
<font size=24>不知我们能否一同出国游览</font>
I wonder if we... I mean Jonathan and l...shall ever see them together.

90
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:09,470
<font size=24>我们来早了,还没人来</font>
We're early, driver. No one is here.

91
00:10:11,470 --> 00:10:13,670
<font size=24>(死人才走的快)</font>

92
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:31,910
<font size=24>城堡远不远?</font>
I say, is the castle far?

93
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:53,400
<font size=24>欢迎光临寒舍</font>
Welcome to my home.

94
00:12:54,570 --> 00:12:57,000
<font size=24>轻松自在地进来</font>
Enter freely of your own will...

95
00:12:57,170 --> 00:12:59,830
<font size=24>将你的欢乐留下</font>
and leave some of the happiness you bring.

96
00:13:00,410 --> 00:13:01,840
<font size=24>德古拉伯爵</font>
Count Dracula?

97
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,940
<font size=24>在下就是</font>
I am...

98
00:13:03,940 --> 00:13:06,000
<font size=24>德古拉</font>
Dracula.

99
00:13:06,180 --> 00:13:09,740
<font size=24>寒舍蓬壁生辉了,哈克先生</font>
And I bid you welcome, Mr. Harker, to my house.

100
00:13:13,190 --> 00:13:14,350
<font size=24>请进</font>
Come in.

101
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:33,540
<font size=24>请恕我</font>
You will, I trust, excuse me that I...

102
00:13:34,210 --> 00:13:36,370
<font size=24>不能奉陪</font>
do not join you.

103
00:13:39,110 --> 00:13:41,950
<font size=24>我已经吃过了</font>
But I have already dined.

104
00:13:43,050 --> 00:13:45,280
<font size=24>而且我从不喝</font>
And I never drink...

105
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:49,280
<font size=24>葡萄酒</font>
wine.

106
00:13:55,230 --> 00:13:58,560
<font size=24>你的祖先? 五官很像</font>
An ancestor? I see a resemblance.

107
00:14:01,070 --> 00:14:03,540
<font size=24>德古拉的徽记</font>
The Order of the Dracul.

108
00:14:05,470 --> 00:14:06,900
<font size=24>是条龙</font>
The Dragon.

109
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:10,140
<font size=24>古代有个社</font>
An ancient society...

110
00:14:10,980 --> 00:14:13,410
<font size=24>我的祖先宣誓入会</font>
pledging my forefathers...

111
00:14:14,750 --> 00:14:18,650
<font size=24>保护教会抵御外侮</font>
to defend their church against all enemies of Christ.

112
00:14:22,160 --> 00:14:25,590
<font size=24>结果却和教会</font>
That relationship was not entirely...

113
00:14:27,190 --> 00:14:28,180
<font size=24>闹僵</font>
successful.

114
00:14:29,330 --> 00:14:31,130
<font size=24>是吗?</font>
Oh, yes.

115
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:37,870
<font size=24>这不是开玩笑的事</font>
It is no laughing matter.

116
00:14:41,310 --> 00:14:43,970
<font size=24>我们德古家值得骄傲</font>
We Draculs have a right to be proud.

117
00:14:44,980 --> 00:14:47,810
<font size=24>不论阿提拉大帝如何残暴</font>
What devil or witch was ever so great as Attila...

118
00:14:47,980 --> 00:14:50,810
<font size=24>我也流着相同的血液</font>
whose blood flows in these veins?

119
00:14:56,220 --> 00:14:57,380
<font size=24>血！</font>
Blood...

120
00:15:02,560 --> 00:15:06,560
<font size=24>这年头成宝了</font>
is too precious a thing in these times.

121
00:15:11,340 --> 00:15:14,500
<font size=24>杀伐的年代已过去</font>
The warlike days are over.

122
00:15:16,410 --> 00:15:19,240
<font size=24>我家族的光荣战迹</font>
The victories of my great race...

123
00:15:20,680 --> 00:15:23,340
<font size=24>只成为故事</font>
are but a tale to be told.

124
00:15:26,690 --> 00:15:30,090
<font size=24>我是最后一名子嗣</font>
I am the last of my kind.

125
00:15:33,090 --> 00:15:35,930
<font size=24>恕我无知,伯爵</font>
I have offended you with my ignorance, Count.

126
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:38,530
<font size=24>原谅我</font>
Forgive me.

127
00:15:51,380 --> 00:15:57,080
<font size=24>我渴望在伦敦拥挤的街道行走</font>
I do so long to go through the crowded streets...of your mighty London...

128
00:15:57,220 --> 00:16:01,120
<font size=24>混在匆忙的人群中</font>
to be in the midst of the whirl and the rush of humanity...

129
00:16:02,120 --> 00:16:04,450
<font size=24>分享它的生命力</font>
to share its life...

130
00:16:04,620 --> 00:16:05,960
<font size=24>它的改变</font>
its changes,

131
00:16:06,130 --> 00:16:07,560
<font size=24>及死亡</font>
its death.

132
00:16:07,730 --> 00:16:10,560
<font size=24>完成了 伯爵</font>
There. You, Count, are...

133
00:16:13,730 --> 00:16:16,130
<font size=24>你是卡费教堂的所有人</font>
are the owner of Carfax Abbey at Purfleet.

134
00:16:16,300 --> 00:16:17,630
<font size=24>恭喜</font>
Congratulations.

135
00:16:18,740 --> 00:16:23,040
<font size=24>贵公司对你赞许有加</font>
Your firm writes most highly...of your talents.

136
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:25,640
<font size=24>他们说你的品味</font>
They say you are a man of good...

137
00:16:27,080 --> 00:16:28,410
<font size=24>很高</font>
taste.

138
00:16:30,580 --> 00:16:33,070
<font size=24>还说你能力不输给</font>
And that you are a worthy substitute...

139
00:16:33,250 --> 00:16:35,410
<font size=24>前任...</font>
to your predecessor,

140
00:16:35,820 --> 00:16:37,980
<font size=24>伦费先生</font>
Mr. Renfield.

141
00:16:38,220 --> 00:16:39,990
<font size=24>你可以相信我</font>
You may rely on me, Count.

142
00:16:40,930 --> 00:16:42,490
<font size=24>恕我好奇</font>
Forgive my curiosity, but why ten houses...

143
00:16:42,730 --> 00:16:46,060
<font size=24>为何十所房子都买在伦敦附近</font>
in such precise locations around London?

144
00:16:46,800 --> 00:16:48,630
<font size=24>炒地皮?</font>
Is it to raise the market value?

145
00:16:51,870 --> 00:16:54,200
<font size=24>你相信宿命吗</font>
Do you believe in destiny?

146
00:16:57,380 --> 00:17:00,040
<font size=24>时间都可因...</font>
That even the powers of time...

147
00:17:01,010 --> 00:17:02,070
<font size=24>某一...</font>
can be altered for

148
00:17:02,720 --> 00:17:05,650
<font size=24>目的而改变?</font>
a single purpose?

149
00:17:14,730 --> 00:17:20,570
<font size=24>找到真爱的人才是...</font>
The luckiest man who walks on this Earth...is the one who finds...

150
00:17:20,570 --> 00:17:22,230
<font size=24>最幸运的人</font>
true love.

151
00:17:23,500 --> 00:17:24,990
<font size=24>你找到米娜了</font>
You found Mina.

152
00:17:25,840 --> 00:17:27,830
<font size=24>我以为丢了呢</font>
I thought she was lost.

153
00:17:28,410 --> 00:17:30,840
<font size=24>我回去后就结婚</font>
We're to be married as soon as I return.

154
00:17:31,740 --> 00:17:33,510
<font size=24>你结婚了吗 伯爵?</font>
Are you married, Count?

155
00:17:35,180 --> 00:17:36,170
<font size=24>先生</font>
Sir...

156
00:17:36,520 --> 00:17:37,780
<font size=24>你结婚了吗?</font>
are you married?

157
00:17:39,690 --> 00:17:41,680
<font size=24>结过一次</font>
I was married once.

158
00:17:42,760 --> 00:17:44,920
<font size=24>多年以前</font>
Ages ago, it seems.

159
00:17:46,260 --> 00:17:47,590
<font size=24>她死了</font>
She died.

160
00:17:50,200 --> 00:17:51,750
<font size=24>真令人难过</font>
I'm very sorry.

161
00:17:52,200 --> 00:17:54,030
<font size=24>是她命好</font>
She was fortunate.

162
00:17:56,770 --> 00:18:00,030
<font size=24>我一生凄凉</font>
My life, at its best, is misery.

163
00:18:05,210 --> 00:18:07,870
<font size=24>她一定会是个贤妻</font>
She will no doubt make a devoted wife.

164
00:18:09,550 --> 00:18:12,110
<font size=24>而你是个忠实的丈夫</font>
