326
00:28:31,870 --> 00:28:35,770
<font size=24>而...川索凡尼亚不同于英国</font>
Transylvania is not England.

327
00:28:36,940 --> 00:28:39,600
<font size=24>我们的风俗习惯与你们不同</font>
Our ways are not your ways.

328
00:28:40,210 --> 00:28:41,700
<font size=24>你一定会</font>
And to you...

329
00:28:42,480 --> 00:28:45,640
<font size=24>觉得很怪异</font>
there shall be many strange things.

330
00:28:45,980 --> 00:28:48,890
<font size=24>我已经看到许多怪事</font>
I've seen many strange things already.

331
00:28:49,220 --> 00:28:52,550
<font size=24>狼群追逐我穿过蓝色炼狱</font>
Bloody wolves chasing me through some blue inferno!

332
00:28:58,060 --> 00:29:00,220
<font size=24>你听听</font>
Listen to them.

333
00:29:04,840 --> 00:29:07,330
<font size=24>夜童的哭号</font>
The children of the night.

334
00:29:09,910 --> 00:29:12,340
<font size=24>多美妙的音乐</font>
What sweet music they make.

335
00:29:13,010 --> 00:29:14,000
<font size=24>音乐</font>
Music?

336
00:29:14,180 --> 00:29:15,670
<font size=24>那群野兽?</font>
Those animals?

337
00:29:49,650 --> 00:29:52,080
<font size=24>我照德古拉的意思写了三封信</font>
I did as Dracula instructed. I wrote three letters.

338
00:29:52,250 --> 00:29:57,150
<font size=24>给公司、家人以及心爱的米娜</font>
To the firm, to my family and to my beloved Mina.

339
00:29:57,590 --> 00:30:00,580
<font size=24>我没提及我的恐惧</font>
I said nothing of my fears as he will read them, no doubt.

340
00:30:05,760 --> 00:30:08,260
<font size=24>因为我知道我成了囚犯</font>
I know now that I am a prisoner.

341
00:31:33,890 --> 00:31:35,080
<font size=24>强纳生！</font>
Jonathan.

342
00:31:36,860 --> 00:31:39,190
<font size=24>强纳生,到我身边</font>
Jonathan, come to me.

343
00:31:48,870 --> 00:31:50,200
<font size=24>来</font>
Come.

344
00:32:09,150 --> 00:32:10,710
<font size=24>躺下</font>
Lay down.

345
00:32:12,220 --> 00:32:14,160
<font size=24>躺在我怀里</font>
Lay back into my arms.

346
00:32:23,800 --> 00:32:25,570
<font size=24>躺下</font>
Lay back, Jonathan.

347
00:34:17,750 --> 00:34:19,180
<font size=24>(你们干嘛)</font>

348
00:34:19,320 --> 00:34:20,310
<font size=24>(冒牌货)</font>

349
00:34:27,390 --> 00:34:29,120
<font size=24>(不准碰他)</font>

350
00:34:29,190 --> 00:34:31,190
<font size=24>(他是我的)</font>

351
00:34:31,730 --> 00:34:33,720
<font size=24>(你从没恋爱过)</font>

352
00:34:36,940 --> 00:34:41,530
<font size=24>(有,我能恋爱)</font>

353
00:34:43,680 --> 00:34:47,740
<font size=24>(而且我将再次恋爱)</font>

354
00:34:56,150 --> 00:34:58,880
<font size=24>(那我们今晚没血喝了吗?)</font>

355
00:35:35,760 --> 00:35:37,920
<font size=24>(葳荷米娜墨瑞,希灵汉庄园)</font>

356
00:35:43,030 --> 00:35:45,730
<font size=24>吾爱米娜：一切均安</font>
"Dearest Mina, all is well here.

357
00:35:46,040 --> 00:35:50,870
<font size=24>伯爵要我住一个月教他英国礼俗</font>
The count has insisted I remain for a month...to tutor him in English custom.

358
00:35:51,310 --> 00:35:54,040
<font size=24>别他无语,只有我爱你</font>
I can say no more, except I love you.

359
00:35:54,750 --> 00:35:57,150
<font size=24>忠实至终的强纳生上</font>
Ever faithful, Jonathan."

360
00:36:00,790 --> 00:36:04,520
<font size=24>这些信让我陷入绝境</font>
The letters I have written have undoubtedly sealed my doom.

361
00:36:08,460 --> 00:36:10,120
<font size=24>伯爵的吉普赛人</font>
The count's gypsies...

362
00:36:10,300 --> 00:36:14,530
<font size=24>英勇战士们  效忠这位贵族,死而无惧</font>
fearless warriors who are loyal to the death to whatever nobleman they serve...

363
00:36:17,400 --> 00:36:19,390
<font size=24>他们日夜工作</font>
day and night they toil,

364
00:36:19,670 --> 00:36:24,500
<font size=24>将城堡的土装箱</font>
filling boxes with decrepit earth...from the bowels of the castle.

365
00:36:25,540 --> 00:36:30,040
<font size=24>运到刚购入的伦敦卡费教堂</font>
They are to be delivered to his newly acquired Carfax Abbey in London.

366
00:36:32,150 --> 00:36:35,050
<font size=24>为什么要装土呢?</font>
Why do they fill these boxes with earth?

367
00:36:41,560 --> 00:36:43,890
<font size=24>我爱他!我爱他</font>
I love him! I love him!

368
00:36:44,530 --> 00:36:46,220
<font size=24>米娜</font>
Mina.

369
00:36:46,900 --> 00:36:49,660
<font size=24>妙不可言,我决定了</font>
It's so wonderful. I've decided.

370
00:36:49,900 --> 00:36:52,500
<font size=24>我爱他,我要嫁他</font>
I love him and I've said yes.

371
00:36:52,670 --> 00:36:54,760
<font size=24>总算!你先别说</font>
Finally. Don't tell me.

372
00:36:54,910 --> 00:36:56,900
<font size=24>带大刀的德州人? 不！</font>
The Texan with the big knife? Oh, no.

373
00:36:57,180 --> 00:36:59,170
<font size=24>我要嫁第三号</font>
To my dear number three.

374
00:36:59,340 --> 00:37:00,900
<font size=24>阿瑟荷伍爵爷</font>
Lord Arthur Holmwood.

375
00:37:01,080 --> 00:37:03,240
<font size=24>荷伍勋爵夫妇</font>
Lord and Lady Holmwood.

376
00:37:03,420 --> 00:37:06,180
<font size=24>你做伴娘,答应吧</font>
You are to be my maid of honor. Oh, say yes.

377
00:37:06,790 --> 00:37:10,080
<font size=24>怎么回事?今天是我大喜</font>
Mina, what is it? It's the most exciting day of my life.

378
00:37:11,890 --> 00:37:13,220
<font size=24>你好像漠不关心</font>
You don't seem to care.

379
00:37:13,860 --> 00:37:17,120
<font size=24>我只是很担心强纳生</font>
It's just that I'm so terribly worried about Jonathan.

380
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:19,630
<font size=24>来信语气冷淡</font>
This letter I received is so...

381
00:37:19,800 --> 00:37:23,390
<font size=24>很不寻常,根本不像他</font>
It's so cold. It's so unnatural. It's not like him at all.

382
00:37:24,740 --> 00:37:26,290
<font size=24>别担心</font>
Mina, don't worry.

383
00:37:52,960 --> 00:37:55,130
<font size=24>丰饶女神号,船长日志</font>
Captain's log: : The Demeter.

384
00:37:55,300 --> 00:37:57,460
<font size=24>1897年6月27日</font>
27thJune, 1897.

385
00:38:00,470 --> 00:38:03,370
<font size=24>我们载了50箱实验用土</font>
We picked up 50 boxes of experimental earth...

386
00:38:03,540 --> 00:38:05,480
<font size=24>前往英国伦敦</font>
bound for London, England.

387
00:38:05,810 --> 00:38:10,840
<font size=24>一场莫名风暴来袭</font>
Set sail at noon into a storm...that seemed to come out of nowhere...

388
00:38:10,950 --> 00:38:13,210
<font size=24>将我们推向汪洋</font>
carrying us out to sea.

389
00:38:34,940 --> 00:38:36,740
<font size=24>(伦敦动物园)</font>

390
00:38:48,350 --> 00:38:50,080
<font size=24>7月3日</font>
Third ofJuly.

391
00:38:50,190 --> 00:38:52,090
<font size=24>第二名船员失踪</font>
Second mate has gone missing.

392
00:38:52,190 --> 00:38:53,850
<font size=24>接近直布罗陀海峡</font>
Nearing Gibraltar.

393
00:38:53,990 --> 00:38:55,430
<font size=24>风暴持续肆虐</font>
Storm continues.

394
00:38:55,590 --> 00:38:57,250
<font size=24>船员非常不安</font>
Crew uneasy.

395
00:38:57,700 --> 00:39:03,190
<font size=24>他们相信船上有鬼魅</font>
Believe someone or something...is aboard the ship with us.

396
00:39:05,670 --> 00:39:07,800
<font size=24>(伦敦)</font>

397
00:39:15,880 --> 00:39:18,010
<font size=24>主人,我在这里！(卡费斯区精神病院)</font>
Master, I am here!

398
00:39:19,020 --> 00:39:21,780
<font size=24>万物之主即将来到</font>
The master of all life is at hand!

399
00:39:22,220 --> 00:39:26,690
<font size=24>来了,我听候差遣,主人</font>
Gather round!I am here to do your bidding, master!

400
00:39:26,690 --> 00:39:29,350
<font size=24>我已遥遥尊奉你许久</font>
I have worshipped you long and far off!

401
00:39:29,560 --> 00:39:32,550
<font size=24>如今你来了,主人</font>
And now you are near, master!

402
00:39:33,300 --> 00:39:35,460
<font size=24>我是你的奴隶</font>
I am your slave!

403
00:39:35,800 --> 00:39:38,130
<font size=24>我等候你的命令</font>
I await your command!

404
00:39:38,470 --> 00:39:41,130
<font size=24>伦费这病人愈来愈有趣</font>
The case of Renfield grows more interesting.

405
00:39:41,370 --> 00:39:43,360
<font size=24>他自有一套想法</font>
Yet, there is method in his madness

406
00:39:43,580 --> 00:39:45,240
<font size=24>他吃苍蝇、蜘蛛</font>
with his flies and spiders.

407
00:39:45,580 --> 00:39:48,710
<font size=24>我若能解开疯人心智之谜</font>
Had I the secret of even one such brilliant mind...

408
00:39:49,250 --> 00:39:51,840
<font size=24>那该有多好</font>
the key to the fancy of one lunatic...

409
00:39:59,060 --> 00:39:59,990
<font size=24>露西</font>
Lucy!

410
00:40:00,530 --> 00:40:02,650
<font size=24>露西！</font>
Lucy!

411
00:40:58,720 --> 00:40:59,840
<font size=24>露西?</font>
Lucy?

412
00:40:59,920 --> 00:41:00,850
<font size=24>露西！</font>
Lucy!

413
00:41:02,030 --> 00:41:03,010
<font size=24>露西！</font>
Lucy!

414
00:41:09,830 --> 00:41:10,960
<font size=24>露西?</font>
Lucy?

415
00:41:44,600 --> 00:41:45,860
<font size=24>露西！</font>
Lucy!

416
00:42:02,220 --> 00:42:03,210
<font size=24>露西！</font>
Lucy!

417
00:42:40,990 --> 00:42:44,790
<font size=24>不!不要看我</font>
No. Do not see me.

418
00:42:57,540 --> 00:42:59,270
<font size=24>露西!露西！</font>
Lucy!Lucy!

419
00:43:01,880 --> 00:43:04,350
<font size=24>我控制不了自己</font>
Oh! I couldn't control myself.

420
00:43:04,550 --> 00:43:07,810
<font size=24>你在做梦,你又梦游了</font>
Hush, Lucy. You're dreaming. You're walking in your sleep again.

421
00:43:07,950 --> 00:43:08,940
<font size=24>我的灵魂</font>
My soul,

422
00:43:09,890 --> 00:43:11,220
<font size=24>出窍了</font>
it seemed to leave my body.

423
00:43:11,720 --> 00:43:15,160
<font size=24>我从没有如此痛苦的感觉</font>
There was this agonizing feeling,

424
00:43:15,390 --> 00:43:17,020
<font size=24>好像魂魄唤不回</font>
and I couldn't get back to it.

425
00:43:17,090 --> 00:43:18,150
<font size=24>我不停地发抖</font>
I'm absolutely shaking.

426
00:43:18,230 --> 00:43:20,630
<font size=24>不要紧,做梦罢了</font>
It's all right. You were dreaming.

427
00:43:20,900 --> 00:43:23,390
<font size=24>狼人诱惑我</font>
I had to. It sort of pulled me and lured me.

428
00:43:23,630 --> 00:43:25,300
<font size=24>我禁不住  没事的</font>
- I had no control. - It's all right.

429
00:43:26,840 --> 00:43:28,700
<font size=24>它双眼血红  别说了</font>
- It had red eyes. - Hush now.

430
00:43:30,310 --> 00:43:32,210
<font size=24>我还尝过它的血</font>
I still have the taste of his blood in my mouth.

431
00:43:40,720 --> 00:43:43,310
<font size=24>(伦敦)</font>

432
00:43:44,320 --> 00:43:46,850
<font size=24>(山姆毕林父子地产公司)</font>

433
00:43:47,060 --> 00:43:49,390
<font size=24>箱子搬过来</font>
Here we go. Swing it round here.

434
00:43:51,660 --> 00:43:53,490
<font size=24>主人</font>
Master.

435
00:43:54,330 --> 00:43:57,600
<font size=24>我听候吩咐(卡费教堂,伦敦)</font>
I am here to do your bidding.

436
00:43:58,200 --> 00:43:59,530
<font size=24>主人</font>
Master!

437
00:44:00,040 --> 00:44:01,700
<font size=24>我在这</font>
I am here!

438
00:44:02,710 --> 00:44:05,040
<font size=24>我膜拜你</font>
I have worshipped you.

439
00:44:07,980 --> 00:44:12,540
<font size=24>与传说相反 吸血鬼,如同夜行动物</font>
Contrary to some beliefs, the vampire...like any other night creature,

440
00:44:12,820 --> 00:44:14,940
<font size=24>白天亦可行动</font>
can move about by day...

441
00:44:15,020 --> 00:44:19,350
<font size=24>但因与其作息时间不同法力也会因而衰退</font>
though it is not his natural time, and his powers are weak.

442
00:44:24,160 --> 00:44:25,650
<font size=24>(动物园的狼只逃出)</font>

443
00:44:25,760 --> 00:44:27,560
<font size=24>(史上最怪异的风暴)</font>

444
00:44:27,660 --> 00:44:30,190
<font size=24>(帆船船员神秘失踪)</font>

445
00:44:35,870 --> 00:44:38,400
<font size=24>好棒的戏院</font>
See the amazing cinematograph!

446
00:44:39,040 --> 00:44:42,030
<font size=24>现代文明的奇能</font>
A wonder of modern civilization!

447
00:44:42,450 --> 00:44:44,210
<font size=24>最新奇观</font>
The latest sensation!

448
00:44:44,610 --> 00:44:47,280
<font size=24>最伟大的壮举</font>
The greatest attraction of the century!

449
00:44:47,980 --> 00:44:50,710
<font size=24>全球新奇观</font>
The new wonder of the world!

450
00:44:52,620 --> 00:44:55,280
<font size=24>(快来戏院哦)</font>

451
00:45:14,910 --> 00:45:16,400
<font size=24>看我</font>
See me.

452
00:45:18,750 --> 00:45:19,980
<font size=24>看着我</font>
See me now.

453
00:45:22,320 --> 00:45:26,420
<font size=24>(最强烈的突起暴风袭击英国)</font>

454
00:45:26,990 --> 00:45:29,750
<font size=24>动物园逃出之狼仍未捕获</font>
Escaped wolf from zoo still at large!

455
00:45:30,130 --> 00:45:31,560
<font size=24>买报纸吧?先生</font>
Buy a paper, sir?

456
00:45:34,260 --> 00:45:35,600
<font size=24>谢谢你,先生</font>
Thank you, sir.

457
00:45:38,270 --> 00:45:40,930
<font size=24>买报纸哦!买报纸</font>
Get your Gazette! Penny a paper!

458
00:45:55,120 --> 00:45:57,280
<font size=24>我最深的歉意</font>
My humblest apologies.

459
00:45:58,690 --> 00:46:01,520
<font size=24>恕我 无知</font>
Forgive my ignorance.

460
00:46:01,960 --> 00:46:08,090
<font size=24>我刚上岸,对贵地一无所知</font>
I am recently arrived from abroad...and I do not know your city.

461
00:46:08,130 --> 00:46:09,890
<font size=24>美女是否可</font>
Is a beautiful lady...

462
00:46:09,970 --> 00:46:12,230
<font size=24>地图一份六便士,日安</font>
A street atlas is sixpence. Good day.

463
00:46:14,870 --> 00:46:16,860
<font size=24>我冒犯你了</font>
I have offended you.

464
00:46:18,680 --> 00:46:21,170
<font size=24>我想看电影</font>
I am only looking for the cinematograph.

465
00:46:21,240 --> 00:46:24,580
<font size=24>听说是文明奇观</font>
I understand it is a wonder of the civilized world.

466
00:46:25,450 --> 00:46:28,280
<font size=24>要寻找文化就去博物馆</font>
If you seek culture, then visit a museum.

467
00:46:28,650 --> 00:46:31,310
<font size=24>伦敦有好几个,失陪</font>
London is filled with them. Excuse me.

468
00:46:35,790 --> 00:46:39,130
<font size=24>(利辛戏院—哈姆雷特)</font>

469
00:46:40,960 --> 00:46:43,520
<font size=24>如此美丽聪慧的女子</font>
A woman so lovely and intelligent...

470
00:46:43,700 --> 00:46:47,360
<font size=24>怎能在伦敦街头踽踽独行</font>
should not be walking the streets of London without her gentleman.

471
00:46:47,540 --> 00:46:49,530
<font size=24>我认识你吗?</font>
Do I know you, sir?

472
00:46:50,870 --> 00:46:53,470
<font size=24>你认识我丈夫吗?</font>
Are you acquainted with my husband?

473
00:46:53,910 --> 00:46:55,710
<font size=24>我叫警察了</font>
Shall I call the police?

474
00:46:57,710 --> 00:46:59,050
<font size=24>丈夫?</font>
Husband?

475
00:46:59,980 --> 00:47:02,320
<font size=24>不打扰了</font>
I shall bother you no more.

476
00:47:06,390 --> 00:47:07,650
<font size=24>先生</font>
Sir.

477
00:47:08,830 --> 00:47:10,880
<font size=24>我失礼了</font>
It is I who have been rude.

478
00:47:11,560 --> 00:47:14,000
<font size=24>若你找</font>
- If you're looking... - Please.

479
00:47:16,730 --> 00:47:19,400
<font size=24>请容我自我介绍</font>
Permit me to introduce myself.

480
00:47:21,340 --> 00:47:23,330
<font size=24>我是罗马尼亚的</font>
I am Prince Vlad

481
00:47:24,070 --> 00:47:25,440
<font size=24>弗拉王子</font>
of Sagite.

482
00:47:28,510 --> 00:47:30,240
<font size=24>王子,真的</font>
- A prince, no less? - I am...

483
00:47:30,510 --> 00:47:33,740
<font size=24>我听凭差遣</font>
your servant.

484
00:47:36,250 --> 00:47:37,850
<font size=24>我叫葳荷米娜墨瑞</font>
Wilhelmina Murray.

485
00:47:41,990 --> 00:47:43,860
<font size=24>我的</font>
I am...

486
00:47:44,590 --> 00:47:46,150
<font size=24>荣幸</font>
honored...

487
00:47:46,700 --> 00:47:48,690
<font size=24>米娜小姐</font>
Madam Mina.

488
00:47:52,600 --> 00:47:53,570
<font size=24>这边</font>
This way.

489
00:48:07,780 --> 00:48:09,120
<font size=24>你好,先生</font>
Hello, sir.

490
00:48:09,390 --> 00:48:12,720
<font size=24>晚安,荷伍先生要我来看露西</font>
Mr. Holmwood asked me to stop by to see Miss Lucy.

491
00:48:13,160 --> 00:48:14,680
<font size=24>是的  先生</font>
Yes, sir.

492
00:48:14,960 --> 00:48:16,450
<font size=24>西渥先生到,露西小姐</font>
Dr. Seward, Miss Lucy.

493
00:48:16,630 --> 00:48:17,460
<font size=24>谢谢</font>
Thank you.

494
00:48:17,530 --> 00:48:18,990
<font size=24>杰克</font>
Oh, Jack!

495
00:48:19,400 --> 00:48:21,190
<font size=24>聪明的杰克</font>
Brilliant Jack.

496
00:48:21,260 --> 00:48:22,600
<font size=24>喜欢吗?</font>
Do you like it?

497
00:48:24,330 --> 00:48:26,670
<font size=24>阿瑟叫你来的吗</font>
Did Arthur put you up to this...

498
00:48:26,840 --> 00:48:30,430
<font size=24>还是你想在我婚前与我独处</font>
or did you want me alone just once before I'm married?

499
00:48:30,940 --> 00:48:33,500
<font size=24>露西,你让我难为情</font>
Lucy, you're embarrassing me.

500
00:48:33,680 --> 00:48:35,510
<font size=24>我以医生身份来此</font>
I'm here as your doctor.

501
00:48:36,450 --> 00:48:38,680
<font size=24>你的未婚夫担心你</font>
Your fiance is very worried about you...

502
00:48:38,850 --> 00:48:43,110
<font size=24>医师的职责是神圣的</font>
and I assure you, a doctor's confidence is sacred.

503
00:48:43,790 --> 00:48:45,850
<font size=24>我要你完全信任我</font>
I must have your complete trust.

504
00:48:50,460 --> 00:48:52,450
<font size=24>救我,杰克</font>
Help me, Jack.

505
00:48:53,860 --> 00:48:56,350
<font size=24>我不知怎么回事</font>
I don't know what's happening to me.

506
00:48:56,970 --> 00:48:58,530
<font size=24>我变了</font>
I'm changing.

507
00:48:59,040 --> 00:49:01,030
<font size=24>我可以感觉到</font>
I can feel it.

508
00:49:02,540 --> 00:49:04,270
<font size=24>我听觉灵敏</font>
I can hear everything.

509
00:49:04,440 --> 00:49:07,540
<font size=24>听得到仆人在房屋另一端私语</font>
I hear the servants at the other end of the house, whispering.

510
00:49:07,710 --> 00:49:11,040
<font size=24>阁楼的老鼠声大如象</font>
I hear mice in the attic, stomping like elephants.

511
00:49:11,980 --> 00:49:14,640
<font size=24>我一直做恶梦</font>
But I'm having horrible nightmares, Jack.

512
00:49:16,890 --> 00:49:18,380
<font size=24>那些眼睛</font>
The eyes.

513
00:49:18,990 --> 00:49:19,980
<font size=24>杰克</font>
Oh, Jack.

514
00:49:20,060 --> 00:49:21,550
<font size=24>有我在,露西</font>
I'm here, Lucy.

515
00:49:21,990 --> 00:49:23,720
<font size=24>谁也伤不了你</font>
Nothing will harm you.

516
00:49:26,660 --> 00:49:28,150
<font size=24>药很有效</font>
Let it work.

517
00:49:30,070 --> 00:49:31,230
<font size=24>谢谢</font>
- Thank you. - Lucy.

518
00:49:32,500 --> 00:49:34,830
<font size=24>杰克,吻我</font>
Oh, Jack, kiss me.

519
00:49:40,080 --> 00:49:42,740
<font size=24>露西小姐真骚</font>
And may I say, Miss Lucy is hotter than a June bride...

520
00:49:42,910 --> 00:49:45,750
<font size=24>她能裸体骑无鞍马</font>
ridin' bareback buck naked in the Sahara.

521
00:49:45,920 --> 00:49:48,680
<font size=24>说话当心点</font>
I would watch my colonial tongue if I were you.

522
00:49:49,250 --> 00:49:50,690
<font size=24>你好,杰克</font>
Hello, Jack.

523
00:49:51,090 --> 00:49:53,350
<font size=24>病人怎样了</font>
And how's our lovely patient today?

524
00:49:53,760 --> 00:49:57,090
<font size=24>老实说我很惶惑</font>
Well, frankly, Arthur, I'm confounded.

525
00:49:57,360 --> 00:50:00,020
<font size=24>你还在替露西小姐担心</font>
Jack, are you still broodin' over Miss Lucy?

526
00:50:00,430 --> 00:50:03,520
<font size=24>我看她神智错乱</font>
I can only conclude it must be something mental.

527
00:50:03,700 --> 00:50:07,030
<font size=24>胡说  你听到没</font>
How very droll. Did you hear that, Quince?

528
00:50:07,270 --> 00:50:11,040
<font size=24>上周他要娶她现在却要让她进疯人院</font>
Last week he wanted to marry her, and now he wants to have her committed.

529
00:50:12,280 --> 00:50:13,770
<font size=24>我们去瞧瞧她</font>
Let's have a look at her.

530
00:50:24,450 --> 00:50:26,790
<font size=24>我也不明白</font>
I'm at a loss, I admit.

531
00:50:27,620 --> 00:50:32,320
<font size=24>我已拍电报给埃布尔汉梵海辛精神哲学家</font>
I've taken the liberty of cabling Abraham Van Helsing...the metaphysician/philosopher.

532
00:50:32,400 --> 00:50:35,230
<font size=24>我看他是个巫医</font>
Sounds like a goddamn witch doctor to me, Jack.

533
00:50:35,470 --> 00:50:39,060
<font size=24>他是疑难杂症权威</font>
Van Helsing knows more about obscure diseases than any man in the world.

534
00:50:39,400 --> 00:50:41,390
<font size=24>也是我的良师</font>
He's my teacher and mentor.

535
00:50:44,570 --> 00:50:45,910
<font size=24>请他来</font>
Do it, man.

536
00:50:46,310 --> 00:50:47,640
<font size=24>带他来此</font>
Bring him here.

537
00:50:48,080 --> 00:50:49,810
<font size=24>不论花多少钱</font>
Spare no expense.

538
00:51:25,010 --> 00:51:26,450
<font size=24>了不起</font>
Astounding.

539
00:51:26,780 --> 00:51:29,450
<font size=24>科学是无止尽的</font>
There are no limits to science.

540
00:51:32,020 --> 00:51:34,620
<font size=24>这哪叫科学</font>
How can you call this science?

541
00:51:35,530 --> 00:51:40,360
<font size=24>居里夫人会同意这看法吗?</font>
Do you think Madam Curie would invite such comparisons?Really.

542
00:51:43,470 --> 00:51:46,130
<font size=24>我不该来的</font>
I shouldn't have come here.

543
00:51:46,800 --> 00:51:48,130
<font size=24>我得走了</font>
I must go.

544
00:51:54,140 --> 00:51:55,540
<font size=24>不要怕我</font>
Do not fear me.

545
00:52:11,230 --> 00:52:12,820
<font size=24>住手</font>
Stop this.

546
00:52:13,200 --> 00:52:14,600
<font size=24>住手！</font>
Stop this.

547
00:52:24,470 --> 00:52:26,810
<font size=24>天啊,你是谁</font>
My God. Who are you?

548
00:52:27,310 --> 00:52:28,900
<font size=24>我认识你</font>
I know you.

549
00:52:29,410 --> 00:52:36,120
<font size=24>我跨越...时间的瀚海来寻你</font>
I have crossed oceans of time...

550
00:53:15,190 --> 00:53:17,130
<font size=24>各位来宾不要惊慌</font>
There is no need to panic.

551
00:53:17,130 --> 00:53:20,620
<font size=24>捕兽师自会处理</font>
The animal handlers have everything under complete control.

552
00:53:41,120 --> 00:53:43,110
<font size=24>过来,米娜</font>
Come here, Mina.

553
00:54:02,140 --> 00:54:03,630
<font size=24>他喜欢你</font>
He likes you.

554
00:54:30,100 --> 00:54:33,030
<font size=24>野兽能教导我们许多事</font>
There is much to be learned from beasts.

555
00:55:31,090 --> 00:55:35,090
<font size=24>(好友濒死,不明原因之血疾)</font>

556
00:55:35,160 --> 00:55:38,960
<font size=24>(我急需协助,杰克西渥)</font>

557
00:55:46,510 --> 00:55:48,770
<font size=24>热带吸血蝙蝠一天</font>
The tropical pampas vampire bat must...

558
00:55:49,280 --> 00:55:53,010
<font size=24>要吸体重十倍的鲜血</font>
consume ten times its own weight in fresh blood each day...

559
00:55:53,850 --> 00:55:56,280
<font size=24>否则它自己会死</font>
or its own blood cells will die.

560
00:56:05,730 --> 00:56:07,320
<font size=24>小混球</font>
Cute little vermin, ja?

561
00:56:08,660 --> 00:56:11,260
<font size=24>我们研究血液及血液疾病</font>
Blood and the diseases of the blood...

562
00:56:11,600 --> 00:56:14,000
<font size=24>如梅毒</font>
such as syphilis, they concern us here.

563
00:56:17,640 --> 00:56:19,370
<font size=24>性病“爱神之疾”</font>
The very name "venereal diseases"...the diseases of Venus,

564
00:56:19,510 --> 00:56:21,200
<font size=24>非常传神</font>
imputes to them divine origin.

565
00:56:21,680 --> 00:56:24,940
<font size=24>牵涉到基督文明</font>
And they are involved in that sex problem about which...

566
00:56:25,080 --> 00:56:29,280
<font size=24>对伦理与性的观念</font>
the ethics and ideals of Christian civilization are concerned.

567
00:56:29,420 --> 00:56:34,150
<font size=24>其实 文明与梅毒几乎同步发展</font>
In fact, civilization and syphilization have advanced together.

568
00:56:37,360 --> 00:56:38,350
<font size=24>这是什么</font>
What is this?

569
00:56:38,530 --> 00:56:40,290
<font size=24>电报,教授</font>
It's from the telegraph, Professor.

570
00:56:40,430 --> 00:56:41,690
<font size=24>电报?</font>
Telegraph?

571
00:56:45,440 --> 00:56:49,200
<font size=24>谢谢  谢谢各位,下课</font>
Thank you. Gentlemen, thank you. That will be all.

572
00:57:00,180 --> 00:57:01,450
<font size=24>黎明时刻</font>
Dawn.

573
00:57:01,650 --> 00:57:04,640
<font size=24>这也许是我最后一篇日记</font>
These may be the last words I write in this journal.

574
00:57:04,820 --> 00:57:07,260
<font size=24>德古拉把我丢给这些妖女</font>
Dracula has left me with these women...

575
00:57:07,420 --> 00:57:09,520
<font size=24>她们喝我的血</font>
these devils of the pit.

576
00:57:09,660 --> 00:57:12,090
<font size=24>让我气息犹存</font>
They drain my blood to keep me weak...

577
00:57:12,260 --> 00:57:14,590
<font size=24>却逃不了</font>
barely alive so I cannot escape.

578
00:57:14,760 --> 00:57:18,100
<font size=24>我今天尝试最后一次逃到水边</font>
I will try one last time today to escape to the water.

579
00:57:18,330 --> 00:57:21,100
<font size=24>一定有路可以通到河边</font>
There must be passageway to the river...

580
00:57:21,270 --> 00:57:23,670
<font size=24>逃出这受诅之地</font>
and then away from this cursed land...

581
00:57:23,870 --> 00:57:26,840
<font size=24>及披着人皮的群魔</font>
where the devil and his children still walk with earthly feet.

582
00:57:37,450 --> 00:57:39,550
<font size=24>我正式宣布</font>
For the record, I do attest...

583
00:57:39,690 --> 00:57:42,890
<font size=24>此刻亚拉汉梵海辛</font>
that at this point, I, Abraham Van Helsing...

584
00:57:43,030 --> 00:57:46,760
<font size=24>亲自调查这些怪事</font>
became personally involved in these strange events.

585
00:58:40,850 --> 00:58:44,180
<font size=24>梵海辛教授,你果然来了</font>
Professor Van Helsing, how good of you to come.

586
00:58:48,620 --> 00:58:51,530
<font size=24>我一向乐于帮助需要我的朋友</font>
I always come to my friends in need when they call me.

587
00:58:51,960 --> 00:58:54,520
<font size=24>把病情详细告诉我</font>
So, Jack, tell me everything about your case.

588
00:58:54,700 --> 00:58:57,690
<font size=24>她有一般贫血症状</font>
She has all the usual physical anemic signs.

589
00:58:57,830 --> 00:58:59,820
<font size=24>血液分析正常</font>
Her blood analyzes normal, and yet it is not.

590
00:59:00,040 --> 00:59:03,270
<font size=24>但事实上她持续失血</font>
She manifests continued blood loss.

591
00:59:03,410 --> 00:59:04,670
<font size=24>我找不出原因</font>
I cannot trace the cause.

592
00:59:04,810 --> 00:59:06,170
<font size=24>失血?怎么会</font>
Blood loss? How?

593
00:59:15,990 --> 00:59:17,320
<font size=24>把门关上</font>
My God, close the doors!

594
00:59:28,830 --> 00:59:29,990
<font size=24>天啊</font>
My God...

595
00:59:30,270 --> 00:59:32,000
<font size=24>她还是个孩子</font>
she's only a child.

596
00:59:33,870 --> 00:59:35,300
<font size=24>是啊</font>
Ja.

597
00:59:36,670 --> 00:59:38,070
<font size=24>老天！</font>
My God.

598
00:59:39,180 --> 00:59:43,410
<font size=24>不得延误立刻输血,脱掉外套</font>
There's no time to lose. There must be a transfusion at once.Take off your coat.

599
00:59:44,280 --> 00:59:46,610
<font size=24>还会绑止血带吧</font>
Remember how to tie a tourniquet?Or have you forgotten?

600
00:59:46,750 --> 00:59:48,080
<font size=24>你精通输血?</font>
You perfected a procedure?

601
00:59:48,520 --> 00:59:52,690
<font size=24>精通?不,我只会蓝斯坦法</font>
Perfected? No. I've only experimented.Landsteiner's method.

602
00:59:54,520 --> 00:59:56,680
<font size=24>只替动物输过,山羊、绵羊啦</font>
Animals, goats, sheeps.

603
00:59:58,260 --> 01:00:02,160
<font size=24>若血清有溶血现象红血球会破裂</font>
If hemolysis occurs in the blood donor serum...her red blood cells will explode.

604
01:00:02,500 --> 01:00:04,590
<font size=24>她就会死,把管子拿好</font>
She will die. Take this tube.

605
01:00:08,700 --> 01:00:10,670
<font size=24>你们在搞什么</font>
What in God's name is going on up here?

606
01:00:10,870 --> 01:00:12,430
<font size=24>这位是梵海辛教授</font>
This is Professor Van Helsing, Art.

607
01:00:12,610 --> 01:00:13,910
<font size=24>他把露西怎么了</font>
What the hell is he doing to Lucy?

608
01:00:14,010 --> 01:00:15,270
<font size=24>救她的命</font>
He's trying to save her life.

609
01:00:15,380 --> 01:00:16,140
<font size=24>老天！</font>
Good God!

610
01:00:16,210 --> 01:00:17,410
<font size=24>你是她的未婚夫</font>
You're the fiance?

611
01:00:17,480 --> 01:00:18,640
<font size=24>请让开</font>
Please.

612
01:00:19,380 --> 01:00:20,610
<font size=24>请！</font>
Please.

613
01:00:21,520 --> 01:00:26,280
<font size=24>外套脱掉,她生命垂危须输血</font>
Take off your coat. This young lady's very ill. She's dying.She wants blood and blood she must have.

614
01:00:26,860 --> 01:00:28,190
<font size=24>外套脱掉！</font>
Take off your coat.

615
01:00:28,390 --> 01:00:29,950
<font size=24>袖子卷起来</font>
Roll up your sleeve, Art.

616
01:00:31,590 --> 01:00:33,720
<font size=24>老天！快！</font>
- Oh, God. - Quickly, quickly.

617
01:00:33,960 --> 01:00:35,290
<font size=24>卷起来</font>
Roll it up!

618
01:00:35,670 --> 01:00:37,460
<font size=24>可能有点痛</font>
This may hurt a little, Art.

619
01:00:49,150 --> 01:00:53,550
<font size=24>请原谅我  她是我的命,最后一滴血都行</font>
Forgive me. My life is hers. I would give my last drop of blood to save her.

620
01:00:53,750 --> 01:00:54,810
<font size=24>最后一滴?</font>
Your last drop?

621
01:00:55,580 --> 01:00:57,810
<font size=24>谢谢,欢迎你</font>
Thank you.You are very welcome here.

622
01:00:57,990 --> 01:00:59,960
<font size=24>我不要那么多</font>
I don't ask as much as that.

623
01:01:00,060 --> 01:01:01,150
<font size=24>目前还不要</font>
Not yet.

624
01:01:01,360 --> 01:01:02,690
<font size=24>握住她的手</font>
Hold her hand.

625
01:01:14,970 --> 01:01:19,540
<font size=24>杰克...她输了两人份的血</font>
Jack, that poor creature has had the blood of two men put into her already.

626
01:01:19,710 --> 01:01:23,300
<font size=24>妈呀!她装不了那么多血</font>
Man alive. Her whole body couldn't hold that much blood.

627
01:01:26,320 --> 01:01:27,680
<font size=24>露西的血去哪呢</font>
What took it out?

628
01:01:27,750 --> 01:01:29,780
<font size=24>问的好,摩里斯先生</font>
That's a good question, Mr. Morris.

629
01:01:35,060 --> 01:01:36,990
<font size=24>喉咙那些痕迹?</font>
Those marks on her throat...

630
01:01:37,230 --> 01:01:41,660
<font size=24>不是疾病或伤痕,而是失血处</font>
no disease, no trituration...I am sure the blood loss occurred there.

631
01:01:42,060 --> 01:01:44,120
<font size=24>血去哪呢?</font>
Oh? Where did the blood go?

632
01:01:45,130 --> 01:01:47,570
<font size=24>你以前是个细心的学生</font>
You were once a careful student, Jack.

633
01:01:47,800 --> 01:01:49,740
<font size=24>用脑呀,血去哪了?告诉我!</font>
Use your brain! Where did the blood go?Tell me!

634
01:01:52,070 --> 01:01:54,470
<font size=24>床铺上有血   没错</font>
- The bed would be covered in blood. - Exactly.

635
01:01:54,810 --> 01:01:59,470
<font size=24>你没观察到不可知的现象</font>
You do not let your eyes see nor your ears hear...that which you cannot account for.

636
01:01:59,650 --> 01:02:03,640
<font size=24>有异物吸她的血后飞走?</font>
Something just went up there, sucked it out of her and flew away?

637
01:02:05,350 --> 01:02:06,910
<font size=24>对 有何不可?</font>
Ja. Why not?

638
01:02:08,020 --> 01:02:11,360
<font size=24>高明,真高明</font>
That's brilliant. That's absolutely brilliant.

639
01:02:11,690 --> 01:02:15,690
<font size=24>请问神医,露西是怎么了?</font>
Will one of you learned doctors... or whatever you are...kindly tell me what is going on with my Lucy?

640
01:02:17,170 --> 01:02:19,600
<font size=24>杰克,你是个科学家</font>
Jack, you are a scientist.

641
01:02:20,040 --> 01:02:24,440
<font size=24>宇宙中可有你不明了的事实?</font>
Do you not think there are things in this universe you cannot understand...and which are true...

642
01:02:24,640 --> 01:02:25,970
<font size=24>像是催眠</font>
mesmerism, hypnotism?

643
01:02:26,110 --> 01:02:27,840
<font size=24>你和夏卡已证实了</font>
You and Charcot have proved hypnotism.

644
01:02:28,040 --> 01:02:30,770
<font size=24>实体与灵体</font>
Materialization, astral bodies.

645
01:02:39,460 --> 01:02:40,790
<font size=24>教授?</font>
Professor?

646
01:02:42,960 --> 01:02:44,190
<font size=24>他去哪了</font>
Where did he go?

647
01:02:47,400 --> 01:02:48,290
<font size=24>看到了吧</font>
You see?

648
01:02:49,400 --> 01:02:51,800
<font size=24>我像是个菜乌</font>
I feel like a blundering novice.

649
01:02:52,070 --> 01:02:54,870
<font size=24>我们对抗的不是疾病</font>
Gentlemen, we're not fighting some disease here.

650
01:02:55,740 --> 01:03:00,040
<font size=24>露西小姐的咬痕是妖魔所致</font>
Those marks on your dear Miss Lucy's neck were made...by something unspeakable out there.

651
01:03:00,040 --> 01:03:01,370
<font size=24>已死又未死</font>
Dead, but not dead.

652
01:03:01,710 --> 01:03:04,610
<font size=24>妖魔追猎我们,原因不明</font>
It stalks us for some dread purpose I do not comprehend.

653
01:03:04,880 --> 01:03:07,640
<font size=24>它吸露西的血维持生命</font>
To live, it feeds on Lucy's precious blood.

654
01:03:07,820 --> 01:03:10,310
<font size=24>是个野兽,怪物</font>
It is a beast, a monster.

655
01:03:28,740 --> 01:03:31,900
<font size=24>我和露西是怎么了</font>
What is happening to Lucy and to me?

656
01:03:32,140 --> 01:03:35,130
<font size=24>年幼时我从不烦躁</font>
When I was younger, my feelings were never troubled.

657
01:03:35,380 --> 01:03:37,570
<font size=24>真希望能恢复往日</font>
I wish I were myself again...

658
01:03:37,750 --> 01:03:40,580
<font size=24>那么敏锐,永可依赖的米娜</font>
the sensible Mina I always depended on.

659
01:03:48,160 --> 01:03:49,750
<font size=24>艾伯森酒</font>
Absinthe...

660
01:03:50,330 --> 01:03:53,160
<font size=24>含春药的成份</font>
is the aphrodisiac of the self.

661
01:03:55,060 --> 01:03:56,760
<font size=24>住在酒里的...</font>
The green fairy...

662
01:03:57,330 --> 01:04:01,070
<font size=24>绿仙子</font>
who lives in the absinthe...

663
01:04:02,470 --> 01:04:04,230
<font size=24>要你的灵魂</font>
wants your soul.

664
01:04:07,080 --> 01:04:08,170
<font size=24>但是</font>
But...

665
01:04:09,850 --> 01:04:11,680
<font size=24>你可以放心</font>
you are safe with me.

666
01:04:27,530 --> 01:04:29,290
<font size=24>王子...</font>
Tell me, Prince...

667
01:04:29,970 --> 01:04:32,090
<font size=24>告诉我你家乡的事</font>
tell me of your home.

668
01:04:34,800 --> 01:04:39,110
<font size=24>全世界最美丽的地方</font>
The most beautiful place...in all creation.

669
01:04:39,940 --> 01:04:43,810
<font size=24>一定是</font>
Yes, it must be.

670
01:04:47,550 --> 01:04:49,880
<font size=24>森林</font>
A land beyond a great,

671
01:04:50,050 --> 01:04:51,450
<font size=24>密布</font>
vast forest...

672
01:04:54,120 --> 01:04:57,120
<font size=24>山峦起伏</font>
surrounded by majestic mountains...

673
01:04:58,790 --> 01:05:00,630
<font size=24>葡萄园</font>
lush vineyards...

674
01:05:02,900 --> 01:05:07,070
<font size=24>遍地无处可比拟的</font>
and flowers of such frailty and beauty...

675
01:05:07,400 --> 01:05:09,840
<font size=24>妖艳花朵</font>
as to be found nowhere else.

676
01:05:19,680 --> 01:05:23,680
<font size=24>你说的好像亲眼看过</font>
You've described my home...as if you had seen it firsthand.

677
01:05:28,090 --> 01:05:30,390
<font size=24>或许受你的声调影响</font>
It's your voice, perhaps.

678
01:05:31,160 --> 01:05:33,090
<font size=24>好熟悉</font>
It's so familiar.

679
01:05:35,400 --> 01:05:36,730
<font size=24>仿佛...</font>
It's like...

680
01:05:38,400 --> 01:05:41,600
<font size=24>梦中无法认出的声音</font>
It's like a voice in a dream I cannot place...

681
01:05:44,270 --> 01:05:46,260
<font size=24>在我孤独时</font>
and it comforts me.

682
01:05:47,110 --> 01:05:48,940
<font size=24>安抚我  在你孤独时</font>
- When I am alone. - When you are alone.

683
01:06:11,470 --> 01:06:13,560
<font size=24>王妃呢?</font>
And what of the princess?

684
01:06:20,380 --> 01:06:21,710
<font size=24>王妃?</font>
Princess?

685
01:06:21,910 --> 01:06:24,240
<font size=24>有王子就有王妃</font>
There is always a princess...

686
01:06:26,150 --> 01:06:28,640
<font size=24>穿着白衣裙</font>
with gowns flowing white.

687
01:06:32,250 --> 01:06:35,820
<font size=24>她的脸</font>
And her face.

688
01:06:36,090 --> 01:06:37,390
<font size=24>天啊</font>
Oh, God...

689
01:06:39,260 --> 01:06:40,730
<font size=24>她的脸</font>
her face...

690
01:06:44,930 --> 01:06:46,200
<font size=24>是条河</font>
is a river.

691
01:06:51,740 --> 01:06:53,400
<font size=24>王妃</font>
The princess...

692
01:06:54,410 --> 01:06:58,810
<font size=24>是条....充满伤痛</font>
she's a river filled with tears of sadness...

693
01:06:59,650 --> 01:07:02,240
<font size=24>心碎泪水的河</font>
and heartbreak.

694
01:07:05,720 --> 01:07:07,660
<font size=24>是有过王妃</font>
There was a princess.

695
01:07:11,330 --> 01:07:12,660
<font size=24>伊丽莎白</font>
Elisabeta.

696
01:07:15,760 --> 01:07:19,930
<font size=24>她是全世界最耀眼的女子</font>
She was the most radiant woman...in all the empires of the world.

697
01:07:27,610 --> 01:07:31,050
<font size=24>谣言拆散了她与王子</font>
Man's deceit took her from her ancient prince.

698
01:07:33,120 --> 01:07:34,610
<font size=24>她投入...</font>
She leapt to her death...

699
01:07:35,220 --> 01:07:38,350
<font size=24>你提到的河而死</font>
into the river that you spoke of.

700
01:07:39,690 --> 01:07:43,050
<font size=24>我的 母语...</font>
In my mother's tongue...

701
01:07:44,060 --> 01:07:49,420
<font size=24>那条河叫</font>
it is called...argesh.

702
01:07:51,500 --> 01:07:53,370
<font size=24>王妃河</font>
River princess.

703
01:09:30,030 --> 01:09:31,260
<font size=24>亲爱的女士</font>
Dear Madam.

704
01:09:31,330 --> 01:09:34,460
<font size=24>你的未婚夫在修道院(阿格莎修女8月12日之信)</font>
Your fiance is safe and in the care...

705
01:09:34,540 --> 01:09:36,940
<font size=24>安然无恙</font>
of the good sisters of the Blessed Sacrament.

706
01:09:38,540 --> 01:09:42,640
<font size=24>哈克先生认为你有生命危险</font>
Mr. Harker believes your life is in extreme danger...

707
01:09:42,840 --> 01:09:46,410
<font size=24>他急切希望你到此</font>
and he desires with all urgency that you join him here...

708
01:09:46,580 --> 01:09:49,420
<font size=24>立刻成婚</font>
so that you may immediately be married.

709
01:09:49,650 --> 01:09:51,880
<font size=24>祝福你</font>
Yours with all blessings,

710
01:09:52,020 --> 01:09:53,850
<font size=24>阿格莎修女上</font>
Sister Agatha.

711
01:09:56,530 --> 01:09:58,320
<font size=24>亲爱的王子</font>
My sweet prince.

712
01:09:59,060 --> 01:10:01,430
<font size=24>绝不能让强纳生知道</font>
Jonathan must never know of us.

713
01:10:09,100 --> 01:10:10,770
<font size=24>露西</font>
Lucy!

714
01:10:10,840 --> 01:10:12,430
<font size=24>我是亚拉汉梵海辛</font>
I'm Abraham Van Helsing.

715
01:10:12,670 --> 01:10:14,010
<font size=24>梵海辛博士</font>
Dr. Van Helsing.

716
01:10:14,180 --> 01:10:17,080
<font size=24>你是米娜小姐,露西的好友?</font>
And you're Madam Mina, dear friend to our Lucy, ja?

717
01:10:17,510 --> 01:10:18,600
<font size=24>她怎样了</font>
How is she, doctor?

718
01:10:18,650 --> 01:10:20,440
<font size=24>仍很虚弱</font>
She's still very weak.

719
01:10:20,750 --> 01:10:25,250
<font size=24>她告诉我你担心你爱的强纳生</font>
She tells me of your beloved Jonathan Harker...and your worry for him.

720
01:10:25,620 --> 01:10:28,280
<font size=24>我为所有的年轻爱侣担心</font>
Well, I, too, worry for all young lovers.

721
01:10:32,460 --> 01:10:34,450
<font size=24>生命中有黑暗</font>
There are darknesses in life, my child...

722
01:10:35,030 --> 01:10:36,960
<font size=24>也有光明</font>
and there are lights.

723
01:10:37,130 --> 01:10:39,790
<font size=24>你便是光明,亲爱的米娜</font>
You are one of the lights, dear Mina...

724
01:10:40,040 --> 01:10:42,230
<font size=24>光明中的光明</font>
the light of all light.

725
01:10:47,710 --> 01:10:49,070
<font size=24>去看你的朋友吧</font>
Go now. See your friend.

726
01:11:05,830 --> 01:11:07,290
<font size=24>米娜</font>
Mina.

727
01:11:10,670 --> 01:11:12,660
<font size=24>你不太一样,米娜</font>
You look different,Mina.

728
01:11:13,440 --> 01:11:16,000
<font size=24>脸上发光</font>
You look positively radiant.

729
01:11:16,610 --> 01:11:18,040
<font size=24>有强纳生的消息</font>
You heard from Jonathan.

730
01:11:18,040 --> 01:11:21,360
<font size=24>是吗?  嗯</font>
- Didn't you? - Yes.

731
01:11:22,010 --> 01:11:23,940
<font size=24>他平安无事,露西</font>
He's safe,Lucy.

732
01:11:24,280 --> 01:11:26,680
<font size=24>在罗马尼亚一家修道院</font>
He's in a convent in Romania.

733
01:11:27,180 --> 01:11:30,170
<font size=24>得了严重的脑热病</font>
He's suffering from a violent brain fever.

734
01:11:30,620 --> 01:11:33,750
<font size=24>修女替他写信</font>
The good sisters are caring for him.They wrote to me,

735
01:11:34,020 --> 01:11:36,080
<font size=24>说他需要我</font>
and they say he needs me...

736
01:11:38,930 --> 01:11:40,090
<font size=24>但....我不去</font>
but I won't go.

737
01:11:40,930 --> 01:11:42,430
<font size=24>我不要丢下你</font>
I'm not going to leave you.

738
01:11:42,500 --> 01:11:43,560
<font size=24>米娜</font>
Mina.

739
01:11:44,970 --> 01:11:47,370
<font size=24>你必须去</font>
You've got to go to him...

740
01:11:47,640 --> 01:11:49,190
<font size=24>你要爱他</font>
and you've got to love him...

741
01:11:50,110 --> 01:11:52,700
<font size=24>立刻嫁给他</font>
and marry him right then and there.

742
01:11:54,310 --> 01:11:56,870
<font size=24>这个你收下</font>
And I want you to take this, my sister.

743
01:11:57,550 --> 01:11:59,410
<font size=24>我送你的贺礼</font>
It's my wedding gift to you.

744
01:11:59,550 --> 01:12:01,020
<font size=24>不,露西</font>
No,Lucy.

745
01:12:01,820 --> 01:12:03,910
<font size=24>别担心任性的小露西</font>
Don't worry about spoiled little Lucy.

746
01:12:06,290 --> 01:12:07,980
<font size=24>我会康复的</font>
I'll be all right.

747
01:12:09,560 --> 01:12:11,860
<font size=24>代我向强纳生致爱</font>
Tell Jonathan oceans of love.

748
01:12:27,510 --> 01:12:28,570
<font size=24>杰克 她怎么了?</font>
Jack, how is she?

749
01:12:47,700 --> 01:12:49,720
<font size=24>我受不了大蒜味</font>
This is why I cannot breathe!

750
01:12:49,800 --> 01:12:51,200
<font size=24>露西 这是药</font>
Lucy, it's medicinal.

751
01:12:51,270 --> 01:12:54,830
<font size=24>会助你睡得好</font>
To help you sleep. To dream better dreams.

752
01:12:55,170 --> 01:12:57,900
<font size=24>只是普通大蒜嘛</font>
It's garlic! It's nothing but common garlic!

753
01:12:58,440 --> 01:13:00,170
<font size=24>昆西来看你了</font>
Quincey's here to see you.

754
01:13:00,340 --> 01:13:01,670
<font size=24>拿点白兰地来</font>
Get some brandy.

755
01:13:01,880 --> 01:13:03,040
<font size=24>露西小姐</font>
Now, Miss Lucy,

756
01:13:03,480 --> 01:13:07,350
<font size=24>你好好休息,阿瑟叫我来看你</font>
you just rest easy.Arthur sent me to take care of you.

757
01:13:08,350 --> 01:13:10,510
<font size=24>他说你不快好,我就得</font>
He said if you don't get better quick...

758
01:13:10,690 --> 01:13:13,090
<font size=24>一枪毙了你,像对跛脚马般</font>
I have to put you out of your misery like a lame horse.

759
01:13:16,090 --> 01:13:18,690
<font size=24>你真野蛮</font>
You're such a beast.

760
01:13:21,700 --> 01:13:23,760
<font size=24>吻我好吗?昆西?</font>
Will you kiss me?Quincey?

761
01:13:26,970 --> 01:13:28,370
<font size=24>吻我</font>
Kiss me.

762
01:13:31,610 --> 01:13:32,600
<font size=24>吻我</font>
Kiss me.

763
01:13:36,240 --> 01:13:38,410
<font size=24>老笨蛋</font>
That old coot!

764
01:13:38,650 --> 01:13:40,240
<font size=24>放开我</font>
Get off me!

765
01:13:40,820 --> 01:13:42,580
<font size=24>露西,听我说</font>
Lucy,Listen to me!

766
01:13:42,820 --> 01:13:44,910
<font size=24>睡觉  快睡觉</font>
Sleep, sleep now. Sleep.

767
01:13:47,360 --> 01:13:49,320
<font size=24>睡吧</font>
You're at peace.

768
01:13:49,320 --> 01:13:50,480
<font size=24>你们看</font>
Look. There. There.

769
01:13:57,070 --> 01:13:58,190
<font size=24>吸血鬼</font>
Nosferatu.

770
01:14:03,670 --> 01:14:06,140
<font size=24>(吸血鬼)</font>

771
01:14:12,280 --> 01:14:14,840
<font size=24>此篇讲述野蛮的</font>
"Here occurs the shocking and frightening history...

772
01:14:15,850 --> 01:14:18,840
<font size=24>德古拉王子骇人野史</font>
of the wild, berserk Prince Dracula...

773
01:14:19,020 --> 01:14:21,010
<font size=24>他将人插住</font>
How he impaled people and roasted them...

774
01:14:21,190 --> 01:14:22,850
<font size=24>烤身、煮头</font>
boiled their heads in a kettle...

775
01:14:23,020 --> 01:14:25,360
<font size=24>活生生的剥皮</font>
how he skinned them alive...

776
01:14:25,530 --> 01:14:28,860
<font size=24>凌迟,饮他们的血</font>
and hacked them to pieces and then drank their blood."

777
01:14:33,770 --> 01:14:35,100
<font size=24>德古拉</font>
Dracul.

778
01:14:36,440 --> 01:14:38,700
<font size=24>血便是生命</font>
For blood is the life.

779
01:14:53,460 --> 01:14:55,390
<font size=24>亲爱的王子</font>
"My dearest Prince,

780
01:14:56,060 --> 01:14:57,390
<font size=24>请原谅我</font>
forgive me.

781
01:14:57,790 --> 01:15:01,060
<font size=24>我收到未婚夫自罗马尼亚的信</font>
I have received word from my fiance in Romania.

782
01:15:01,460 --> 01:15:04,730
<font size=24>我要去见他并完婚</font>
I am en route to join him. We are to be married.

783
01:15:06,000 --> 01:15:07,990
<font size=24>永不再见</font>
I will never see you again.

784
01:15:08,600 --> 01:15:09,930
<font size=24>米娜上</font>
Mina."

785
01:15:19,850 --> 01:15:24,980
<font size=24>奇怪,那位怪友好像也跟来了</font>
It is odd, but I feel almost...that my strange friend is with me.

786
01:15:25,090 --> 01:15:27,610
<font size=24>他在我的思绪中</font>
He speaks to me in my thoughts.

787
01:15:27,760 --> 01:15:31,090
<font size=24>与他在一起我最有活力</font>
With him I felt more alive than ever I had.

788
01:15:31,530 --> 01:15:34,020
<font size=24>如今他不在,又将成婚</font>
And now without him, soon to be a bride...

789
01:15:34,200 --> 01:15:36,690
<font size=24>我深感困惑失落</font>
I feel confused and lost.

790
01:15:37,370 --> 01:15:40,530
<font size=24>也许我虽想做好,其实很坏</font>
Perhaps, though I try to be good, I am bad.

791
01:15:41,370 --> 01:15:44,200
<font size=24>或许我是个善变的坏女人</font>
Perhaps I am a bad, inconstant woman.

792
01:16:03,330 --> 01:16:04,720
<font size=24>飓风！</font>
Winds!

793
01:16:05,730 --> 01:16:07,320
<font size=24>飓风！</font>
Winds!

794
01:16:09,360 --> 01:16:12,490
<font size=24>刮大风吧！</font>
Winds!

795
01:16:15,500 --> 01:16:17,060
<font size=24>就是这原因</font>
It is the cause.

796
01:16:17,740 --> 01:16:20,000
<font size=24>就是它</font>
It is the cause of my soul!

797
01:16:20,680 --> 01:16:22,170
<font size=24>天啊!德古拉</font>
It is Dracula...

798
01:16:22,510 --> 01:16:24,070
<font size=24>这个僵尸</font>
the undead...

799
01:16:24,410 --> 01:16:27,280
<font size=24>我一生追击的敌人</font>
the foe I have pursued all my life.

800
01:16:31,690 --> 01:16:33,620
<font size=24>德古拉!</font>
Dracula!

801
01:16:36,190 --> 01:16:38,850
<font size=24>杰克,快有好多事要告诉你</font>
Jack, hurry! I have much to tell you.

802
01:16:41,100 --> 01:16:43,090
<font size=24>小心守候</font>
Guard her well, Mr. Morris.

803
01:16:43,300 --> 01:16:45,360
<font size=24>今晚不得失误</font>
Do not fail here tonight.

804
01:16:45,530 --> 01:16:50,860
<font size=24>我们对抗的是超越凡人的法力</font>
We are dealing with forces beyond all human experience...an enormous power, so guard her well.

805
01:16:51,210 --> 01:16:54,900
<font size=24>若不尽责你的露西将会成女妖</font>
Otherwise your precious Lucy will become a bitch of the devil...

806
01:16:54,980 --> 01:16:56,770
<font size=24>邪恶的魔女</font>
a whore of darkness!

807
01:16:58,850 --> 01:17:00,370
<font size=24>老疯子</font>
You're a sick old buzzard.

808
01:17:02,050 --> 01:17:03,780
<font size=24>听清楚,小子</font>
Hear me out, young man.

809
01:17:03,950 --> 01:17:06,590
<font size=24>露西不是意外所致</font>
Lucy is not a random victim attacked by mere accident.

810
01:17:06,590 --> 01:17:08,250
<font size=24>明白了吗?   不</font>
Do you understand? No.

811
01:17:08,320 --> 01:17:12,320
<font size=24>她自愿受其蛊惑</font>
She is a willing recruit, a breathless, wanton follower.

812
01:17:12,490 --> 01:17:14,890
<font size=24>忠实的门徒</font>
I dare say, a devoted disciple.

813
01:17:15,060 --> 01:17:17,550
<font size=24>她是魔鬼的姘妇</font>
She is the devil's concubine!

814
01:17:19,500 --> 01:17:20,660
<font size=24>懂了吗</font>
Do you understand me?

815
01:17:22,140 --> 01:17:25,700
<font size=24>但我们仍可救回她的魂</font>
Yet, we may still save her precious soul.

816
01:17:26,010 --> 01:17:30,470
<font size=24>但...得先填饱肚子,杰克</font>
But not on an empty stomach.

817
01:17:30,750 --> 01:17:31,730
<font size=24>杰克  是的,先生</font>
- Jack! - Here, sir.

818
01:17:32,680 --> 01:17:35,010
<font size=24>我饿死了,快跟我去吃</font>
I starve. Feed me.

819
01:17:35,920 --> 01:17:37,210
<font size=24>老傻子！</font>
You old coot!

820
01:19:52,310 --> 01:19:55,640
<font size=24>无能的人类跟愚蠢的驱邪物</font>
Your impotent men with their foolish spells...

821
01:19:55,810 --> 01:19:59,370
<font size=24>保护不了你</font>
cannot protect you from my power.

822
01:20:12,190 --> 01:20:14,990
<font size=24>我诅咒你成为僵尸</font>
I condemn you to living death...

823
01:20:15,760 --> 01:20:18,430
<font size=24>永远</font>
to eternal hunger...

824
01:20:19,100 --> 01:20:23,270
<font size=24>嗜饮...鲜血</font>
for living blood.

825
01:21:47,890 --> 01:21:48,880
<font size=24>杰克</font>
Jack!

826
01:21:56,960 --> 01:21:59,160
<font size=24>我知道你深爱她</font>
I know how deeply you loved her.

827
01:21:59,370 --> 01:22:01,100
<font size=24>所以你得相信</font>
That is why you must trust me and believe.

828
01:22:01,170 --> 01:22:03,160
<font size=24>叫我如何相信?</font>
Believe? How can I believe?

829
01:22:03,440 --> 01:22:07,270
<font size=24>你在天黑前带解剖刀来</font>
I want you to bring me, before nightfall, a set of postmortem knives.

830
01:22:07,440 --> 01:22:09,200
<font size=24>解剖?露西</font>
An autopsy? Lucy?

831
01:22:09,380 --> 01:22:13,040
<font size=24>不算,我要割她的头挖她的心</font>
No, not exactly. I just want to cut off her head and take out her heart.

832
01:22:20,820 --> 01:22:23,450
<font size=24>9月17日,日记</font>
Diary, 17th September.

833
01:22:23,720 --> 01:22:25,320
<font size=24>可怜的强纳生</font>
Poor Jonathan.

834
01:22:25,660 --> 01:22:27,460
<font size=24>他仍重病</font>
He's still so ill.

835
01:22:27,660 --> 01:22:30,560
<font size=24>但回到伦敦他很开心</font>
He's cheered by the familiar streets in London.

836
01:22:31,000 --> 01:22:34,990
<font size=24>而我,因露西已死反而难过</font>
For me, now that Lucy is dead, it is a sad homecoming.

837
01:22:36,340 --> 01:22:39,000
<font size=24>仿佛部份的我也已死去</font>
It is as if a part of me is dead too...

838
01:22:39,140 --> 01:22:41,900
<font size=24>除了暗盼</font>
except for the tiny hope that lives in me...

839
01:22:42,080 --> 01:22:44,570
<font size=24>能再见到我的王子</font>
that I will again see my prince.

840
01:22:44,750 --> 01:22:46,240
<font size=24>他在伦敦吗?</font>
Is he here?

841
01:22:47,350 --> 01:22:48,480
<font size=24>我已结婚,</font>
Now that I am married...

842
01:22:48,480 --> 01:22:52,590
<font size=24>才明白对萦绣山中的他</font>
I begin to understand the nature of my feelings for my strange friend...

843
01:22:52,590 --> 01:22:54,920
<font size=24>是怎样的情绪</font>
who is always in my thoughts.

844
01:23:06,170 --> 01:23:08,100
<font size=24>强纳生,怎么了?</font>
Jonathan, what is it?

845
01:23:08,270 --> 01:23:10,170
<font size=24>就是他</font>
It is the man himself.

846
01:23:10,700 --> 01:23:12,430
<font size=24>他变年轻了</font>
Look, he's grown young.

847
01:23:56,280 --> 01:23:57,610
<font size=24>各位</font>
Gentlemen,

848
01:23:58,750 --> 01:24:00,820
<font size=24>非掘露西的墓不可吗?</font>
must we desecrate poor Lucy's grave?

849
01:24:00,820 --> 01:24:02,760
<font size=24>她死得够惨了</font>
She died horribly enough.

850
01:24:05,460 --> 01:24:08,690
<font size=24>若她已死则无碍</font>
If Miss Lucy is dead, then no wrong can be done to her.

851
01:24:08,900 --> 01:24:10,450
<font size=24>若没死</font>
But if she's not dead...

852
01:24:11,470 --> 01:24:13,700
<font size=24>你是说她被活埋?</font>
What are you saying, man? That she's been buried alive?

853
01:24:14,230 --> 01:24:16,860
<font size=24>不,我只是说</font>
No. All I say is

854
01:24:17,300 --> 01:24:18,790
<font size=24>她没死</font>
she is undead.

855
01:24:19,970 --> 01:24:21,130
<font size=24>没死</font>
Undead.

856
01:24:21,480 --> 01:24:23,030
<font size=24>这真疯狂</font>
This is insane.

857
01:24:42,400 --> 01:24:44,620
<font size=24>各位 动手吧</font>
Gentlemen, shall we?

858
01:24:44,830 --> 01:24:47,230
<font size=24>一、二、三</font>
One, two, three.

859
01:25:04,590 --> 01:25:05,920
<font size=24>她呢?</font>
Where is she?

860
01:25:07,920 --> 01:25:09,410
<font size=24>她呢?</font>
Where is she?

861
01:25:10,760 --> 01:25:12,090
<font size=24>你把她怎么了</font>
What have you done with her?

862
01:25:13,760 --> 01:25:18,430
<font size=24>她住在上帝恩典不及之处飘荡在黑暗界</font>
She lives beyond the grace of God...a wanderer in the outer darkness.

863
01:25:18,430 --> 01:25:21,230
<font size=24>她是吸血鬼</font>
She is vampyre, nosferatu.

864
01:25:22,340 --> 01:25:27,100
<font size=24>这些怪物被吸血后不会死</font>
These creatures do not die like the bee after the first sting...

865
01:25:27,270 --> 01:25:30,270
<font size=24>反受传染而成不朽</font>
but instead grow strong and become immortal...once infected by another nosferatu.

866
01:25:35,780 --> 01:25:37,340
<font size=24>所以,吾友</font>
So my friends,

867
01:25:37,520 --> 01:25:39,780
<font size=24>我们不是对抗一个怪物</font>
we fight not one beast...

868
01:25:39,850 --> 01:25:44,850
<font size=24>而是长久流传以血为生的族群</font>
but legions that go on age after age after age...feeding on the blood of the living.

869
01:25:50,200 --> 01:25:52,460
<font size=24>快躲起来</font>
Quickly, hide. Now.

870
01:26:21,500 --> 01:26:22,960
<font size=24>露西</font>
Lucy!

871
01:26:23,360 --> 01:26:24,090
<font size=24>露西</font>
Lucy!

872
01:26:29,900 --> 01:26:32,000
<font size=24>来,阿瑟</font>
Come to me, Arthur.

873
01:26:33,440 --> 01:26:36,340
<font size=24>扔下其它人,来我这里</font>
Leave these others and come to me.

874
01:26:38,350 --> 01:26:41,280
<font size=24>我好想拥抱你</font>
My arms are hungry for you, my darling.

875
01:26:42,420 --> 01:26:45,080
<font size=24>吻我,抱我</font>
Kiss me and caress me...

876
01:26:45,390 --> 01:26:47,580
<font size=24>我亲爱的丈夫,我求你</font>
my darling husband, please.

877
01:26:47,820 --> 01:26:50,350
<font size=24>我们有十字架和圣水</font>
We wave Christ and His holy blood!

878
01:26:50,660 --> 01:26:53,180
<font size=24>我们在主内坚强</font>
We are strong in the Lord and

879
01:26:53,360 --> 01:26:56,520
<font size=24>主赋与我们力量</font>
the power of His might!

880
01:26:57,760 --> 01:27:01,360
<font size=24>主赋与我们力量</font>
The power of God is upon us!

881
01:27:01,540 --> 01:27:04,200
<font size=24>主赋与我们力量</font>
The power of God is upon us!

882
01:27:06,010 --> 01:27:08,130
<font size=24>主赋与我们力量</font>
The power of God is upon us!

883
01:27:11,810 --> 01:27:14,370
<font size=24>我将你带至光明</font>
I bring you from shadow into light!

884
01:27:14,880 --> 01:27:19,110
<font size=24>黑暗王子,我将你逐至地狱</font>
I cast you out, the prince of darkness...into hell!

885
01:27:22,160 --> 01:27:24,760
<font size=24>只需片刻勇气,</font>
A moment's courage, and it is done.

886
01:27:24,760 --> 01:27:26,690
<font size=24>左手拿凿子</font>
Take the stake in your left hand...

887
01:27:28,630 --> 01:27:30,560
<font size=24>对准心脏</font>
place the point over the heart.

888
01:27:35,400 --> 01:27:37,630
<font size=24>奉主之名,敲下去</font>
Then in God's name, strike. Do it now!

889
01:27:53,520 --> 01:27:55,080
<font size=24>吃呀,大餐</font>
Eat, feast.

890
01:27:55,590 --> 01:27:58,250
<font size=24>将来你们需要力气</font>
You'll need your strength for the dark days ahead.

891
01:27:58,930 --> 01:27:59,920
<font size=24>米娜</font>
Mina?

892
01:28:01,430 --> 01:28:02,590
<font size=24>博士 嗯?</font>
- Doctor? - Ja?

893
01:28:04,330 --> 01:28:05,820
<font size=24>露西怎么死的？</font>
How did Lucy die?

894
01:28:09,200 --> 01:28:10,290
<font size=24>这个...</font>
Well...

895
01:28:12,110 --> 01:28:13,540
<font size=24>她死前痛苦吗？</font>
Was she in great pain?

896
01:28:13,940 --> 01:28:16,270
<font size=24>是的,我们砍掉她的头</font>
Ja, she was in great pain. Then we cut off her head...

897
01:28:16,610 --> 01:28:19,880
<font size=24>在心脏钉下十字架,她就安息了</font>
and drove a stake through her heart and burned it and then she found peace.

898
01:28:20,010 --> 01:28:23,010
<font size=24>博士  拜托别说了</font>
Doctor! Please.

899
01:28:26,950 --> 01:28:28,290
<font size=24>哈克先生</font>
So, Mr. Harker...

900
01:28:29,120 --> 01:28:32,020
<font size=24>身为你的医生,问你个</font>
I must now ask you, as your doctor...

901
01:28:34,900 --> 01:28:36,390
<font size=24>敏感问题</font>
a sensitive question.

902
01:28:36,560 --> 01:28:40,560
<font size=24>你和那些怪物在一起时</font>
During your infidelity with those creatures...those demonic women...

903
01:28:40,700 --> 01:28:42,950
<font size=24>可曾吃过</font>
did you, for one instant,

904
01:28:42,970 --> 01:28:44,300
<font size=24>她们的血</font>
taste of their blood?

905
01:28:45,840 --> 01:28:46,500
<font size=24>没有</font>
No!

906
01:28:50,780 --> 01:28:51,510
<font size=24>没有?</font>
No?

907
01:28:52,710 --> 01:28:53,700
<font size=24>没有</font>
No!

908
01:28:56,150 --> 01:28:57,280
<font size=24>很好</font>
Good!

909
01:28:57,780 --> 01:29:02,620
<font size=24>那你没染上露西那种病</font>
Then you have not infected your blood with the terrible...disease that destroyed poor Lucy.

910
01:29:11,400 --> 01:29:13,660
<font size=24>博士,你要知道</font>
Doctor, you must understand.

911
01:29:15,400 --> 01:29:17,560
<font size=24>以前我疑幻似真</font>
I doubted everything...

912
01:29:17,900 --> 01:29:19,570
<font size=24>甚至以为自己疯了</font>
even my mind.

913
01:29:19,640 --> 01:29:21,800
<font size=24>终日恐惧</font>
I was impotent with fear.

914
01:29:22,310 --> 01:29:23,400
<font size=24>我知道  但是</font>
- I know. - But, sir...

915
01:29:23,580 --> 01:29:28,470
<font size=24>我知道吸血鬼睡在哪</font>
I know where the bastard sleeps.

916
01:29:28,650 --> 01:29:30,310
<font size=24>我把他带到</font>
I brought him there,

917
01:29:30,750 --> 01:29:32,410
<font size=24>卡费教堂</font>
to Carfax Abbey.

918
01:29:35,220 --> 01:29:37,750
<font size=24>吸血鬼的确存在</font>
Vampires do exist.

919
01:29:38,830 --> 01:29:41,820
<font size=24>我们围攻的这一个</font>
And this one we fight, this one we face...

920
01:29:42,100 --> 01:29:44,660
<font size=24>有二十人的力气</font>
has the strength of 20 or more people...

921
01:29:44,830 --> 01:29:46,890
<font size=24>你可以证明</font>
and you can testify for that, Mr. Harker.

922
01:29:47,600 --> 01:29:52,240
<font size=24>他能控制低等的蝙蝠、鼠狼</font>
But he can also control the meaner things of life...the bat, the rodent, the wolf.

923
01:29:52,240 --> 01:29:56,440
<font size=24>可化为烟雾遁形</font>
He can appear as mist, as vapor, as fog and vanish at will.

924
01:29:57,580 --> 01:29:59,510
<font size=24>德古拉法力很大,</font>
Now, all these things Dracula can do...

925
01:29:59,510 --> 01:30:01,180
<font size=24>但他不自由</font>
but he is not free.

926
01:30:01,180 --> 01:30:04,580
<font size=24>他必须躺在故土中增加魔力</font>
He must rest in the sacred earth of his homeland to gain his evil power.

927
01:30:04,750 --> 01:30:07,690
<font size=24>我们必须在此将他毁灭</font>
It is here that we must find him and destroy him utterly.

928
01:30:08,590 --> 01:30:11,850
<font size=24>我替这个伯爵难过</font>
I almost feel pity for anything so hunted as this count.

929
01:30:11,990 --> 01:30:13,980
<font size=24>你怎会怜悯这种怪物</font>
How can you pity such a creature?

930
01:30:15,960 --> 01:30:17,290
<font size=24>我带米娜去我的医院</font>
I'll take Mina to my quarters.

931
01:30:17,700 --> 01:30:19,430
<font size=24>你在那儿才安全</font>
Good. You'll be safer there.

932
01:30:23,000 --> 01:30:26,100
<font size=24>子弹伤不了他,</font>
Mr. Morris, your bullets will not harm him.

933
01:30:26,270 --> 01:30:28,540
<font size=24>一定得砍头 我建议你用猎刀</font>
He must be beheaded. I suggest you use your big bowie knife.

934
01:30:28,710 --> 01:30:31,700
<font size=24>我不打算贴近他,博士</font>
Well, I wasn't plannin' on getting that close, Doc.

935
01:30:32,810 --> 01:30:34,210
<font size=24>主人！</font>
Master!

936
01:30:35,950 --> 01:30:37,380
<font size=24>主人</font>
Master!

937
01:30:38,950 --> 01:30:40,350
<font size=24>主人...</font>
Master!

938
01:30:50,960 --> 01:30:52,730
<font size=24>杰克大夫</font>
Dr. Jack!

939
01:30:53,500 --> 01:30:56,660
<font size=24>我获准得永生</font>
I've been promised eternal life!

940
01:30:58,840 --> 01:30:59,830
<font size=24>杰克</font>
Dr. Seward,

941
01:30:59,910 --> 01:31:01,460
<font size=24>那人是谁</font>
who is that man?

942
01:31:01,640 --> 01:31:04,040
<font size=24>那是伦费先生,你不适合久留</font>
Mr. Renfield. This is no place for you, Madam Mina.

943
01:31:04,240 --> 01:31:07,640
<font size=24>伦费?我得见他</font>
Renfield? I must see him.

944
01:31:08,420 --> 01:31:09,970
<font size=24>伦费先生</font>
Mr. Renfield,

945
01:31:10,420 --> 01:31:11,980
<font size=24>别乱来</font>
behave yourself.

946
01:31:14,320 --> 01:31:16,260
<font size=24>这位是哈克太太</font>
This is Mrs. Harker.

947
01:31:17,990 --> 01:31:19,250
<font size=24>晚安</font>
Good evening.

948
01:31:19,430 --> 01:31:21,330
<font size=24>晚安,伦费先生</font>
Good evening, Mr. Renfield.

949
01:31:21,860 --> 01:31:24,520
<font size=24>我太调皮了</font>
It seems I've been rather naughty.

950
01:31:27,200 --> 01:31:28,530
<font size=24>我认识你</font>
I know you.

951
01:31:29,000 --> 01:31:30,940
<font size=24>你是主人的新娘</font>
You're the bride my master covets.

952
01:31:33,540 --> 01:31:35,770
<font size=24>我有丈夫了</font>
I have a husband.

953
01:31:36,210 --> 01:31:37,870
<font size=24>我是哈克太太</font>
I am Mrs. Harker.

954
01:31:39,210 --> 01:31:41,740
<font size=24>我的主人提过你</font>
My master tells me about you.

955
01:31:43,280 --> 01:31:44,610
<font size=24>他怎么说?</font>
What does he tell you?

956
01:31:45,720 --> 01:31:47,450
<font size=24>说他要来</font>
That he is coming.

957
01:31:48,960 --> 01:31:51,010
<font size=24>他要来找你</font>
That he is coming for you.

958
01:31:51,260 --> 01:31:54,190
<font size=24>过来点</font>
Oh, please.

959
01:32:00,170 --> 01:32:02,190
<font size=24>别留在这</font>
Don't stay here.

960
01:32:02,870 --> 01:32:05,360
<font size=24>离开这些人</font>
Get away from these men,

961
01:32:05,640 --> 01:32:06,970
<font size=24>求求你</font>
please.

962
01:32:08,580 --> 01:32:12,310
<font size=24>我祈求主不要再见到你</font>
And I pray to God I may never see your sweet face again.

963
01:32:16,150 --> 01:32:18,810
<font size=24>愿主祝福保佑你</font>
And may the Lord bless and keep you.

964
01:32:30,260 --> 01:32:31,750
<font size=24>主人！</font>
Master!

965
01:32:32,170 --> 01:32:33,500
<font size=24>主人</font>
Master!

966
01:32:33,930 --> 01:32:36,600
<font size=24>你答应我让我永生的</font>
You promised me eternal life...

967
01:32:37,070 --> 01:32:39,770
<font size=24>你却给了这名美女</font>
but you give it to the pretty woman!

968
01:32:40,270 --> 01:32:41,600
<font size=24>杰克大夫</font>
Dr. Jack!

969
01:32:42,340 --> 01:32:44,330
<font size=24>我不是疯子</font>
I'm no lunatic man!

970
01:32:44,510 --> 01:32:47,410
