I have wanted this to happen.

990
01:36:11,520 --> 01:36:13,510
<font size=24>我都知道了</font>
I know that now.

991
01:36:15,320 --> 01:36:18,380
<font size=24>我要永远和你在一起</font>
I want to be with you always.

992
01:36:19,060 --> 01:36:21,860
<font size=24>你不明白自己在说什么</font>
You cannot know what you are saying.

993
01:36:23,660 --> 01:36:25,720
<font size=24>是的</font>
Yes...

994
01:36:25,870 --> 01:36:27,530
<font size=24>我知道</font>
I do know.

995
01:36:40,750 --> 01:36:44,150
<font size=24>我怕再也感受不到你的触摸</font>
I feared I would never feel your touch again.

996
01:36:44,480 --> 01:36:46,750
<font size=24>我以为你死了</font>
I thought you were dead.

997
01:36:53,990 --> 01:36:58,220
<font size=24>这躯壳里没有生命</font>
There is no life in this body.

998
01:37:02,070 --> 01:37:03,730
<font size=24>但你活着</font>
But you live.

999
01:37:05,640 --> 01:37:07,230
<font size=24>你是活的</font>
You live.

1000
01:37:09,340 --> 01:37:11,170
<font size=24>你到底是什么?</font>
What are you?

1001
