I am...

1003
01:37:26,530 --> 01:37:27,860
<font size=24>什么都不是</font>
nothing.

1004
01:37:28,860 --> 01:37:30,520
<font size=24>没有生命</font>
Lifeless.

1005
01:37:32,030 --> 01:37:33,360
