Hear me.

1010
01:37:45,480 --> 01:37:47,040
<font size=24>我是</font>
I am the monster...

1011
01:37:47,250 --> 01:37:50,150
<font size=24>众人皆欲杀之的怪物</font>
that breathing men would kill.

1012
01:37:51,280 --> 01:37:53,620
<font size=24>我就是德古拉</font>
I am Dracula.

1013
