you must die to your breathing life...

1022
01:39:07,260 --> 01:39:09,270
<font size=24>在我的世界重生</font>
and be reborn to mine.

1023
01:39:10,500 --> 01:39:12,660
<font size=24>你永远是我的爱</font>
You are my love...

1024
01:39:13,930 --> 01:39:16,400
<font size=24>与生命</font>
and my life always.

1025
01:39:24,340 --> 01:39:25,400
<font size=24>那么...</font>
Then...

1026
01:39:26,180 --> 01:39:28,510
<font size=24>我将让你永生</font>
I give you life eternal...

1027
01:39:30,680 --> 01:39:32,510
<font size=24>给你长久不息的爱</font>
everlasting love...

1028
01:39:34,190 --> 01:39:37,280
<font size=24>教你 呼风唤雨</font>
the power of the storm...

1029
01:39:38,290 --> 01:39:40,620
<font size=24>降兽驯禽</font>
and the beasts of the earth.

1030
01:39:41,860 --> 01:39:43,420
<font size=24>跟我走</font>
Walk with me...

1031
01:39:44,030 --> 01:39:48,090
<font size=24>永远为我爱妻</font>
to be my loving wife forever.

1032
01:39:48,270 --> 01:39:49,630
<font size=24>我愿意</font>
I will. Yes. Yes.

1033
01:40:21,870 --> 01:40:24,800
<font size=24>喝下去 同我迈入</font>
Drink and join me...

1034
01:40:26,210 --> 01:40:28,200
<font size=24>永生</font>
in eternal life.

1035
01:40:41,920 --> 01:40:45,260
<font size=24>不,我不能害你</font>
I cannot let this be.

1036
01:40:46,990 --> 01:40:49,620
<font size=24>我不在乎,占有我吧</font>
Please, I don't care. Make me yours.

1037
01:40:49,760 --> 01:40:54,220
<font size=24>米娜,你将让我永世</font>
You will be cursed as I am to walk in the shadow of death...

1038
01:40:54,900 --> 01:40:56,770
<font size=24>被诅咒</font>
for all eternity.

1039
01:40:57,840 --> 01:41:00,500
<font size=24>我太爱你</font>
I love you too much...

1040
01:41:01,310 --> 01:41:02,600
<font size=24>而不能害你</font>
to condemn you.

1041
01:41:03,840 --> 01:41:07,970
<font size=24>带我远离死亡阴影</font>
Then take me away from all this death.

1042
01:41:54,090 --> 01:41:55,420
<font size=24>米娜</font>
Mina.

1043
01:42:05,570 --> 01:42:08,130
<font size=24>你以为十字架</font>
You think you can destroy me...

1044
01:42:08,570 --> 01:42:10,740
<font size=24>可以杀死我?</font>
with your idols?

1045
01:42:14,310 --> 01:42:16,510
