Sacred blood of Christ!

1046
01:42:16,750 --> 01:42:19,310
<font size=24>我服侍十字架</font>
I, who served the cross.

1047
01:42:19,850 --> 01:42:22,180
<font size=24>在数百年前</font>
I, who commanded nations...

1048
01:42:22,360 --> 01:42:24,950
<font size=24>我曾领导万军</font>
hundreds of years before you were born.

1049
01:42:25,290 --> 01:42:27,280
<font size=24>你的军队溃败</font>
Your armies were defeated.

1050
01:42:28,030 --> 01:42:29,360
<font size=24>你折磨...</font>
You tortured and

