impaled thousands of people.

1052
01:42:31,800 --> 01:42:34,960
<font size=24>我被背弃</font>
I was betrayed.

1053
01:42:35,230 --> 01:42:36,570
<font size=24>看...</font>
Look

1054
01:42:36,700 --> 01:42:38,290
<font size=24>你的上帝</font>
what your God...

1055
01:42:38,570 --> 01:42:40,970
<font size=24>如何对待我</font>
has done to me.

1056
01:42:41,310 --> 01:42:45,040
<font size=24>你与上帝的战争已结束  伏法吧</font>
No, your war with God is over. You must pay for your crimes.

1057
01:42:49,480 --> 01:42:50,810
<font size=24>基督制伏你</font>
Christ compels you!

1058
01:42:50,980 --> 01:42:52,920
<font size=24>现在她是...</font>
She is now...

1059
01:42:54,550 --> 01:42:57,890
<font size=24>我的新娘了</font>
my bride!

1060
01:43:02,730 --> 01:43:03,990
<font size=24>灯火</font>
More light!

1061
01:43:06,130 --> 01:43:07,330
<font size=24>灯火</font>
Light!

1062
01:43:08,400 --> 01:43:09,660
<font size=24>不够</font>
More light!

1063
01:43:16,740 --> 01:43:19,840
<font size=24>好脏</font>
Unclean.

1064
