<font size=24>捉住那些老鼠</font>
- Get them! - This way!

1065
01:43:22,350 --> 01:43:23,710
<font size=24>得烧掉</font>
- Get them! - They must be found.

1066
01:43:23,880 --> 01:43:24,870
<font size=24>好脏</font>
Unclean.

1067
01:43:25,550 --> 01:43:27,490
<font size=24>我们学到很多</font>
We have learned something much.

1068
01:43:27,750 --> 01:43:29,480
<font size=24>德古拉怕我们</font>
Dracula fears us.

1069
01:43:29,660 --> 01:43:31,210
<font size=24>他怕时间</font>
He fears time.

1070
01:43:31,420 --> 01:43:34,220
<font size=24>否则何必匆匆逃走</font>
For, if not, why does he hurry so?

1071
01:43:34,760 --> 01:43:36,750
<font size=24>他走了</font>
He is gone.

1072
01:43:37,560 --> 01:43:39,000
<font size=24>你怎么知道?</font>
How do you know?

1073
01:43:40,100 --> 01:43:42,430
<font size=24>他告诉我的</font>
He speaks to me.

1074
01:43:44,100 --> 01:43:46,500
<font size=24>他和你心灵相通</font>
He has a strong mind connection to you.

1075
01:43:48,610 --> 01:43:51,540
<font size=24>他的心脏强壮,熬的住死亡</font>
His heart was strong enough to survive the grave.

1076
01:43:52,880 --> 01:43:54,810
<font size=24>你赞赏他</font>
- You admire him. - Ja.

1077
01:43:56,820 --> 01:43:59,680
<font size=24>他生前是个伟人</font>
He was, in life, a most remarkable man...

1078
01:44:00,690 --> 01:44:03,350
<font size=24>思虑恢宏</font>
and his mind was great and powerful...

1079
01:44:03,560 --> 01:44:06,460
<font size=24>但更重要的是</font>
but greater is the necessity to stamp him out...

1080
01:44:06,630 --> 01:44:08,750
<font size=24>让他永不超生</font>
and destroy him utterly.

1081
01:44:09,660 --> 01:44:11,600
<font size=24>博士  嗯?</font>
- Doctor? - Ja?

1082
01:44:14,730 --> 01:44:17,500
<font size=24>我知道我愈来愈像他</font>
I know that I am becoming like him.

1083
01:44:18,500 --> 01:44:20,970
<font size=24>你的救赎是他的毁灭</font>
Your salvation is his destruction.

1084
01:44:22,070 --> 01:44:24,910
<font size=24>所以我要催眠你</font>
That is why I want to hypnotize you.

1085
01:44:25,850 --> 01:44:28,250
<font size=24>我要你及时</font>
I want you to help me find him before it is too late.

1086
01:44:28,750 --> 01:44:32,840
<font size=24>助我找到他  请帮我找到他</font>
Please, help me find him. Please.

1087
01:44:33,650 --> 01:44:35,420
<font size=24>看这烛光</font>
Look into this light...

1088
01:44:36,090 --> 01:44:38,850
<font size=24>光明中的光明</font>
the light of all light, into this flame.

1089
01:44:40,090 --> 01:44:41,920
<font size=24>你双眼沉重</font>
Your eyes are heavy.

1090
