<font size=24>你想睡觉  睡吧</font>
You want to sleep. Sleep now.

1091
01:44:49,470 --> 01:44:51,100
<font size=24>睡吧</font>
Sleep.

1092
01:44:51,200 --> 01:44:54,140
<font size=24>我要去找他,他在叫我</font>
I must go to him.He calls.

1093
01:44:55,680 --> 01:44:57,010
<font size=24>你听到什么</font>
What do you hear?

1094
01:44:59,510 --> 01:45:01,950
<font size=24>听到什么</font>
What do you hear, child?

1095
01:45:03,050 --> 01:45:05,750
<font size=24>听到什么</font>
What do you hear?

1096
01:45:06,950 --> 01:45:09,290
<font size=24>我的王子在呼唤我</font>
Oh, my prince is calling me.

1097
01:45:09,790 --> 01:45:13,780
<font size=24>他飘洋过海</font>
He is traveling across icy seas to his beloved home.

1098
01:45:14,590 --> 01:45:17,260
<font size=24>回家滋长力量</font>
There he will grow strong again.

1099
01:45:17,860 --> 01:45:21,130
<font size=24>我要去找他分享他的力量</font>
I am coming to him to partake of his strength.

1100
01:45:27,510 --> 01:45:32,070
<font size=24>我们当晚在波涛中航过英吉利海峡</font>
We left London by train and crossed the English Channel in stormy seas...

1101
01:45:32,410 --> 01:45:35,400
<font size=24>风浪无疑是伯爵的杰作</font>
no doubt from the passage of the count's ship.

1102
01:45:35,850 --> 01:45:37,750
<font size=24>他呼风唤雨</font>
He commands the winds,

1103
01:45:37,950 --> 01:45:40,080
<font size=24>但我们仍占上风</font>
but we still have the advantage.

1104
01:45:40,290 --> 01:45:43,850
<font size=24>搭火车三天内可抵达瓦纳</font>
By train, we can reach the Romanian port at Varna in three days.

1105
01:45:44,290 --> 01:45:46,550
<font size=24>搭船至少要一周</font>
By ship, it will take him at least a week.

1106
01:45:48,030 --> 01:45:51,020
<font size=24>从巴黎经阿尔卑斯至布达佩斯</font>
From Paris, we traveled through the Alps to Budapest.

1107
01:45:51,200 --> 01:45:55,860
<font size=24>伯爵一定得经直布罗陀 我们已派人看守</font>
The count must sail around the Rock of Gibraltar...where we have posted a lookout...

1108
01:45:56,040 --> 01:45:58,700
<font size=24>至黑海瓦纳港</font>
and then on to the Black Sea port in Varna...

1109
01:45:58,870 --> 01:46:02,100
<font size=24>我们在瓦纳与他碰头将船烧毁</font>
where we will meet his ship and burn it into the sea.

1110
01:46:08,350 --> 01:46:11,650
<font size=24>回家</font>
Home. Home.

1111
01:46:21,390 --> 01:46:24,330
<font size=24>吸血鬼以血为她受洗</font>
The vampire's baptized her with his own blood...

1112
01:46:24,500 --> 01:46:26,160
<font size=24>她已成吸血鬼</font>
and her blood is dying, my friend.

1113
01:46:26,830 --> 01:46:28,390
