It is no use.

1114
01:46:40,750 --> 01:46:43,840
<font size=24>我不让你只身入险地</font>
I will not let you go into the unknown alone.

1115
01:46:44,120 --> 01:46:48,450
<font size=24>可怜的强纳生</font>
Oh, my poor, dear Jonathan.

1116
01:46:48,650 --> 01:46:51,090
<font size=24>我对不起你</font>
Oh, what have I done to you?

1117
01:46:52,760 --> 01:46:55,850
<font size=24>不,是我害了我们俩</font>
No, I have done this to both of us.

1118
01:46:56,030 --> 01:46:58,430
<font size=24>我听到他了,他接近了</font>
I can hear him. He's coming closer.

1119
01:46:58,600 --> 01:47:00,830
