Stay with me.

1122
01:47:06,740 --> 01:47:07,670
<font size=24>求求你</font>
Please.

1123
01:47:07,910 --> 01:47:09,400
<font size=24>我好冷</font>
I am so cold.

1124
01:47:22,050 --> 01:47:23,210
<font size=24>上车</font>
All aboard!

1125
01:47:23,460 --> 01:47:27,650
<font size=24>正午,荷伍接到公司的电报</font>
Noon. Holmwood received a wire from his clerk at Lloyd's.

1126
01:47:27,790 --> 01:47:32,390
<font size=24>伯爵的船在夜雾中赶过我们</font>
The count's ship sailed past us in the night fog...to the northern port of Galatz.

1127
01:47:32,570 --> 01:47:35,400
<font size=24>这个魔鬼在探索米娜的思想</font>
The black devil is reading Mina's mind.

1128
